NK014(pha)006:0: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba khro bo'i dbang gi cho ga
NK014(pha)006:1: khrag 'thung rdo rje'i gad rgyangs zhes bya ba bzhugs
NK014(pha)006:2: so // sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba khro bo bsdus pa'i
NK014(pha)006:3: dbang gi cho ga khrag 'thung rdo rje'i gad rgyangs
NK014(pha)006:4: so // zhes bya ba / bcom ldan 'das dgyes
NK014(pha)006:5: pa chen po badz+ra he ru ka la phyag 'tshal
NK014(pha)006:6: so // zhes bya ba / lo // tshad med thugs rje'i gter mnga' gtan gyi skyabs //
NK014(pha)006:7: rigs dang dkyil 'khor kun gyi khyab bdag mchog /
NK014(pha)006:9: dpal ldan bla ma'i zhabs zung gtsug gis mchod //
NK014(pha)006:10: nges gsang theg pa'i yang rtse snying po'i bcud //
NK014(pha)006:11: gnas lugs de bzhin nyid ston nges pa'i lam //
NK014(pha)006:12: khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad dkyil 'khor du //
NK014(pha)006:13: gzhug thabs rdo rje'i gad rgyangs dbyangs su len //
NK014(pha)006:14: de la 'dir he ru ka 'dus pa'i rgyud las /
NK014(pha)006:15: dang po sa yi cho ga ste //
NK014(pha)006:16: gnyis pa la ni sta gon gnas //
NK014(pha)006:17: gsum pa 'jug pa'i cho ga bya //
NK014(pha)006:19: nub dang po sa'i cho ga dang /
NK014(pha)006:20: gnyis pa sta gon gyi cho ga gzhan rnams rje
NK014(pha)006:21: bla mas mdzad pa'i dkyil chog rdo rje'i phreng ba
NK014(pha)006:22: ltar bya zhing / 'dir slob ma lhag par gnas
NK014(pha)006:23: pa'i cho ga ni dkyil 'khor gyi shar lhor man+dala
NK014(pha)006:24: khru gang pa la 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa bri
NK014(pha)006:25: ltar bya zhing / / slob dpon gyi drung du
NK014(pha)006:26: so shing sogs 'og tu dgos pa'i yo byad thams
NK014(pha)006:28: de nas slob bu rnams khrus bya /
NK014(pha)006:30: srung 'khor bsgom rjes chos bshad thun mong pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK014(pha)006:32: 'di ni sde snod dang rgyud thams cad kyi rtsa
NK014(pha)006:33: ba'am 'phro gzhi lta bur gyur pa dpal sgyu 'phrul
NK014(pha)006:34: d+r+wa ba chen po'i chos kyi rnam grangs te /
NK014(pha)006:35: de la'ang smin grol gyi rim pa gnyis su yod pa las /
NK014(pha)006:36: 'dir smin byed kyi dbang nyid bskur ba skabs su babs pa yin zhing /
NK014(pha)006:37: dbang de la'ang sbyor dngos rjes gsum las /
NK014(pha)006:38: skabs 'dir sbyor ba sta gon gyi bye brag slob
NK014(pha)006:39: ma lhag par gnas pa'i chos rnams sgrub par byed
NK014(pha)006:40: pa yin pas / de'i slad du thog mar khyed
NK014(pha)006:41: rang rnams kyi lus longs spyod dus gsum dang 'brel
NK014(pha)006:42: ba'i dge tshogs rgya mtsho dang bcas pa thams cad
NK014(pha)006:43: gcig tu bsdoms nas 'bul ba'i mos 'dun bgyis te
NK014(pha)006:46: de nas slob ma rnams kyis sems bskyed par bya ste /
NK014(pha)006:48: dang po kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems bskyed pa'i don du 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK014(pha)006:49: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK014(pha)006:50: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK014(pha)006:51: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba las //
NK014(pha)006:52: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK014(pha)006:54: gnyis pa don dam byang chub tu sems bskyed pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:55: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK014(pha)006:56: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK014(pha)006:57: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK014(pha)006:58: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK014(pha)006:59: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK014(pha)006:60: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK014(pha)006:63: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK014(pha)006:64: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK014(pha)006:65: gnas pa med las thams cad gnas //
NK014(pha)006:66: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK014(pha)006:67: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK014(pha)006:68: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK014(pha)006:69: dmigs pa med las thams cad dmigs //
NK014(pha)006:70: dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK014(pha)006:71: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK014(pha)006:72: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK014(pha)006:76: de'i lan du slob dpon gyis /
NK014(pha)006:77: e ma'o bde gshegs snying po las //
NK014(pha)006:78: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis sprul //
NK014(pha)006:79: sna tshogs lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK014(pha)006:80: gnas dang sdug bsngal la sogs pa //
NK014(pha)006:81: bdag dang bdag gir so sor 'dzin //
NK014(pha)006:82: sus kyang ma bcings bcings med de //
NK014(pha)006:83: bcing bar bya ba yod ma yin //
NK014(pha)006:84: rnam rtog bdag tu 'dzin pa yis //
NK014(pha)006:85: nan gyis mkha' la mdud pa dor //
NK014(pha)006:86: bcings med rnam par grol med pa'i //
NK014(pha)006:87: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK014(pha)006:88: khyod la rab tu bstan par bya //
NK014(pha)006:90: skabs 'dir dkyil 'khor gyi don bshad pa la nges shes bskyed par bya ste /
NK014(pha)006:96: gnas skabs bdun du snying po len //
NK014(pha)006:97: bkod pa gang rdzogs de ngo bo //
NK014(pha)006:98: zhes pas bkod pa lha'i 'khor lor rdzogs par snang ba'o //
NK014(pha)006:100: man+da la'i sgra las snying po 'dzin pa'am snying po len pa'i don dang /
NK014(pha)006:101: yang na zlum po'am bskor ba'i don gyis dkyil 'khor ro //
NK014(pha)006:104: 'grel chung las bcu gnyis su phye yang /
NK014(pha)006:105: skabs 'dir bdun du dbye ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK014(pha)006:108: gzugs brnyan lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan gsum //
NK014(pha)006:110: byang chub sems dang tshogs mchog bstan //
NK014(pha)006:112: 'dir 'jug bya'i dkyil 'khor ni lhag pa gzugs brnyan te /
NK014(pha)006:113: 'di lta bu'i gsang sngags bla na med pa'i dkyil
NK014(pha)006:114: 'khor 'di 'dra mthong ba tsam gyis kyang bskal pa
NK014(pha)006:115: bye ba du mar bsags pa'i sdig sgrib 'dag pa
NK014(pha)006:116: sogs kyi phan yon dang ldan na zhugs shing dbang
NK014(pha)006:117: bskur bas ni lta ci smos te /
NK014(pha)006:118: de'i phyir dga' spro yang dag par bskyed mdzod //
NK014(pha)006:120: de nas slob mas gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:121: he ru ka dpal khyod la 'dud //
NK014(pha)006:122: thar lam chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK014(pha)006:123: de nyid dbang dang dam tshig dang //
NK014(pha)006:124: mgon po dpa' bor skyabs song ste //
NK014(pha)006:125: theg chen khang par gzhug pa dang //
NK014(pha)006:126: mkhyen rab ye shes bdag la stsol //
NK014(pha)006:128: de nas gnang ba sbyin cing drang ba ni /
NK014(pha)006:129: bu 'dir shog cig ci bde bar //
NK014(pha)006:130: las spyod rim par 'gro ba dang //
NK014(pha)006:131: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje zung //
NK014(pha)006:132: rdzogs pa'i ye shes bde chen la //
NK014(pha)006:133: dmigs pa med par gnas phyir du //
NK014(pha)006:134: ser sna spangs pa'i dwangs yid kyis //
NK014(pha)006:135: gtong zhing rang sems brtan por bzung //
NK014(pha)006:136: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rdzogs dbang sbyin //
NK014(pha)006:137: zhes gnang ba sbyin zhing lag gi rdo rjes drangs la /
NK014(pha)006:138: khyad par can gyi don la gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:139: bdag ni las mchog skal bar ldan //
NK014(pha)006:140: deng nas theg pa chen po la //
NK014(pha)006:141: brtan par bya phyir bdag la ni //
NK014(pha)006:142: ye shes bsrung ba mdzad du gsol //
NK014(pha)006:144: de nas bgegs bskrad cing sgrib pa phral ba la /
NK014(pha)006:148: tshe mi yar bar bya ba'i phyir dbang phyug gi
NK014(pha)006:149: thugs ka'i sa bon las yi ge b+h+r+aum re slob
NK014(pha)006:152: zhes brjod pas dung khang zla gam dmar po'i gzhal
NK014(pha)006:153: yas khang gnam sgo gcig pa sgo khyud can gcig
NK014(pha)006:154: tu gyur / de'i nang du h+aum yig mthing skya dang /
NK014(pha)006:155: sgor h+aum yig ljang nag gcig gsal ba las 'od 'phros lus kyi nang gang /
NK014(pha)006:156: +aa yu h+aum dzah 'od zer tshur 'dus tshe bcud thams cad dbus kyi h+aum la thim pa las /
NK014(pha)006:157: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)006:158: ces brjod pas h+aum k+aa ra mthing skya rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams pa gcig tu gyur /
NK014(pha)006:159: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)006:160: ces pas sgo'i h+aum yig de mi g.yo ba ljang
NK014(pha)006:161: nag ral gri dang sdigs mdzub can gcig tu gyur
NK014(pha)006:162: te srung ba'i las mdzad par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)006:165: sgrib pa phral ba gnyis kyi /
NK014(pha)006:167: slob dpon zhe sdang rdo rje'i snyems pas /
NK014(pha)006:168: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la phata phata phata /
NK014(pha)006:169: ha la ha la ha la h'u /
NK014(pha)006:170: zhes brjod pas sprul pa'i khro tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa spros /
NK014(pha)006:171: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad gang /
NK014(pha)006:172: ltas chen po bco lnga dang /
NK014(pha)006:173: chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul chen pos bdud bgegs log
NK014(pha)006:174: par 'dren pa'i tshogs thams cad bsdigs bskrad brlag par
NK014(pha)006:176: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)006:177: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:178: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:179: chos can rgyu 'bras bslu ba med pa'i bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:180: khyad par du'ang bcom ldan 'das sgyu 'phrul rnam par
NK014(pha)006:181: rol pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi bden
NK014(pha)006:182: pa dang / bden pa chen po'i byin gyi rlabs kyis /
NK014(pha)006:183: zhes bden stobs brjod pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK014(pha)006:184: 'dir 'dus pa'i slob bu rnams la gdon cing 'tshe
NK014(pha)006:185: ba'i 'byung po thams cad 'dir ma gnas par dengs
NK014(pha)006:187: h+aum bzhi pa'i sngags lan gsum sogs brjod cing gu gul gyis bdug /
NK014(pha)006:189: slar yang khro bo rnams tshur 'dus phyogs mtshams thams
NK014(pha)006:190: cad khro bo dang rdo rje'i gur khang mtshon cha'i
NK014(pha)006:191: char 'bab cing / 'bar ba me'i phreng ba phyogs
NK014(pha)006:192: kun tu 'phro bas bcings te cis kyang mi shigs
NK014(pha)006:193: char 'bab cing / par bsam / gnyis pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:194: slob dpon gyi lag pa g.yas kyi sor mo lnga
NK014(pha)006:195: la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor re re'i steng du h+aum
NK014(pha)006:197: g.yon gyi sor mo lnga la zla ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK014(pha)006:198: re re'i steng du m+aum l+aam m+aam p+aam t+aam rnams
NK014(pha)006:199: kyis mtshan pa rigs lnga yab yum bcur gyur bar
NK014(pha)006:206: rigs lnga yab yum mnyam par sbyor bar bsam /
NK014(pha)006:207: gong ltar bden stobs brjod pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK014(pha)006:208: slob bu 'di rnams kyi rgyud la yod pa'i las kyi sgrib pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:209: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:211: lta ba dman pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:212: chos kyis phongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:213: bag chags ngan pa'i sgrib pa la sogs te sgrib
NK014(pha)006:214: pa'i phung po ji snyed pa thams cad phyag rgya'i
NK014(pha)006:217: zhes mang du brjod cing phyag rgya sprugs pas /
NK014(pha)006:218: rigs lnga'i sbyor mtshams nas byang chub sems kyi 'od
NK014(pha)006:219: zer 'phros pas slob bu'i sgrib pa mtha' dag bsregs
NK014(pha)006:220: shing sbyangs / dung khang gi khro bo gnyis kyang
NK014(pha)006:221: zhu lugs su thim pa'i rkyen gyis bu'i lus kyang
NK014(pha)006:222: 'od du zhu ba'i 'od phung gser zhun ma lta
NK014(pha)006:224: de nas slob bu lhar bskyed pa la bskur brlab go bgo lus bsrung bya ba ni /
NK014(pha)006:225: slob dpon gyi h+aum zhes brjod pas 'od phung de nyid h+aum yig mthing nag tu gyur /
NK014(pha)006:228: 'phro 'dus rdo rje rtse dgu bar gyur /
NK014(pha)006:231: slar yang 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las he
NK014(pha)006:232: ru ka mthing nag rdo rje dang dung khrag can
NK014(pha)006:233: du gyur / so so'i phyag rgya slob ma'i mgo bo'i gnas lngar bzhag la /
NK014(pha)006:234: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)006:242: zhes brjod cing rdo rje gnas gsum du gtugs pas byin gyis brlab /
NK014(pha)006:243: slar yang rdo rje rtse lnga'i rgyas bcings pa gnas gsum du bzhag la /
NK014(pha)006:244: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)006:248: byin gyis brlabs pa'i rtags su gnas gsum du sku
NK014(pha)006:249: gsung thugs rdo rje'i lha rang rtags sa bon gyis
NK014(pha)006:250: mtshan pa 'dzin pas rgyas btab par bsam /
NK014(pha)006:251: spyi bor ham bkod pa zhu ba las lus thams cad rdo rje'i go chas bcings par bltas la /
NK014(pha)006:252: rdo rje go cha'i phyag rgya spyi bor 'ching zhing /
NK014(pha)006:253: badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi rak+sha ham /
NK014(pha)006:255: mdzub mo g.yas g.yon gnyis su dang trum las rdo
NK014(pha)006:256: rje gnod sbyin dang mi 'chi thabs sbyor bskyed la
NK014(pha)006:262: spyi bo rnams su rim par mdzub mo gnyis bsnol ba reg pas /
NK014(pha)006:263: gnas de dang der khro bo gnyis po zhabs bsnol
NK014(pha)006:264: nas zhal phyir gzigs te bsrung ba'i las mdzad pa'i
NK014(pha)006:265: thugs ka nas rdo rje'i lu gu rgyud byung bas
NK014(pha)006:267: de nas so shing sbyin pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:268: so shing sor bcu gnyis pa dri bzang gis byugs
NK014(pha)006:269: shing rtse mor me tog gi phreng ba bcings pa
NK014(pha)006:270: slob ma rnams kyi dngos grub kyi ltas brtag pa'i
NK014(pha)006:271: nus pa dang ldan par bsam la sbyin zhing /
NK014(pha)006:272: des kyang mkha' dbyings kyi rgyas bzung la sos 'cha'
NK014(pha)006:273: zhing drud pa ltar byas pas sdig sgrib thams cad
NK014(pha)006:276: zhes man+dala gyi steng du dor bas /
NK014(pha)006:279: mtshams bzhir dngos grub dman pa 'grub par bstan /
NK014(pha)006:280: de nas 'khyor chu blud pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:283: zhes bzlas pa khyor bar blugs la /
NK014(pha)006:284: sarba sam sho d+ha na ye h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)006:285: ces brjod cing 'thung du bcug nas lhag mas kha lag bkru /
NK014(pha)006:286: de nas srung skud 'ching ba ni /
NK014(pha)006:287: srung skud dmar po sum sgril la /
NK014(pha)006:288: bamg+h+n+aam ta krita a mri ta kun+da l+ai tshin+d+ha tshin+d+ha h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)006:289: ces brjod cing mdud pa gsum btab pas byin gyis brlabs la pho'i dpung pa g.yon dang /
NK014(pha)006:292: ces mdud pa'i steng du srin lag gis dri'i thig
NK014(pha)006:293: le byas pas rdo rje'i go khrab kyis g.yogs te
NK014(pha)006:294: rdo rje rgya gram gyi mdud pa spyi mgrin snying
NK014(pha)006:295: kha lte ba gsang gnas rkang mthil dang drug tu
NK014(pha)006:296: byas te bar chad kyi bgegs kyis mi tshugs par
NK014(pha)006:297: bsam / de nas ku sha sbyin pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:298: ku sha'i chun po che chung gnyis rmi lam mi 'khrugs pa'i nus ldan du bsam la /
NK014(pha)006:300: zhes sngas dang stan gyi don du slob dpon gyis
NK014(pha)006:301: phyag g.yas g.yon bsnol te byin pa slob mas kyang
NK014(pha)006:303: de'i rjes su dngos grub kyi snod skyon ngo shes
NK014(pha)006:304: pa'i phyir du dbang gi gegs brgyad bshad par bya
NK014(pha)006:305: ste / sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos grub mchog /
NK014(pha)006:306: dbang dang byin rlabs 'byung ba ni //
NK014(pha)006:307: dper na dwangs pa'i rgya mtsho la //
NK014(pha)006:310: byin rlabs dbang mchog thob pa'i gegs //
NK014(pha)006:311: rnam pa brgyad du rgyal bas bshad //
NK014(pha)006:312: ston pa sngon byon slob dpon la //
NK014(pha)006:313: bka' gcog brnyas par byed pa ni //
NK014(pha)006:314: dbang dang dngos grub dang po'i gegs //
NK014(pha)006:315: bla med 'gro ba'i rdo rje spun //
NK014(pha)006:316: 'khu ldog gdung ba'i sems med na //
NK014(pha)006:317: dbang dang dngos grub gnyis pa'i gegs //
NK014(pha)006:318: byang chub sems la 'dud med cing //
NK014(pha)006:319: thar lam 'dren pa'i lha spong ba //
NK014(pha)006:320: dbang dang byin rlabs gsum pa'i gegs //
NK014(pha)006:321: snying rje'i yul gyur sems can la //
NK014(pha)006:322: thag pa gcod pa bzhi pa'i gegs //
NK014(pha)006:323: gsang bas gsang ba'i lta spyod rnams //
NK014(pha)006:324: yongs la 'byin pa gegs lnga yin //
NK014(pha)006:325: thar lam ston la 'dud med cing //
NK014(pha)006:326: ser snas bcings pa drug pa'i gegs //
NK014(pha)006:327: gzu lum dbang byed las la spyod //
NK014(pha)006:328: dngos grub myur ba'i gegs bdun pa //
NK014(pha)006:329: 'dod pas khe grags lhur len cing //
NK014(pha)006:330: gsang ba'i dam tshig spong ba ste //
NK014(pha)006:331: 'di ni brgyad pa'i gegs su bstan //
NK014(pha)006:332: nyes pa 'di dag spong ba ni //
NK014(pha)006:333: dngos grub dbang gi snod du 'gyur //
NK014(pha)006:334: bu kye nangs par 'dri byed pas //
NK014(pha)006:335: dkyil 'khor steng du legs par nyol //
NK014(pha)006:336: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha sa ma ya damsh+ta h+aum /
NK014(pha)006:337: zhes las bum gyi chus gtor nas /
NK014(pha)006:338: do nub seng ge'i nyal thabs kyis bde bar nyol
NK014(pha)006:339: la mtshan mo'i thun gsum pa tho rengs kyi dus
NK014(pha)006:340: su rmi lam bzang ngan gang rmis pa de nangs
NK014(pha)006:343: slob bu rmi lam ngan pa rmis pa rnams rdo rje gnod sbyin gyi sngags /
NK014(pha)006:345: zhes pa dang mche ba'i phyag rgyas bsrung /
NK014(pha)006:346: kun rmi lam ngan na drag po'i sbyin sreg sogs kyang bya'o //
NK014(pha)006:347: de la rmi lam bzang ngan ni /
NK014(pha)006:351: sku gsung thugs kyi rten mthong ba la sogs pa rmis na bzang /
NK014(pha)006:353: g.yang sa dang ri dang ljon shing las lhung ba /
NK014(pha)006:355: bong bu dang spre'u sogs zhon nas lhor 'gro ba sogs mthong na ngan no //
NK014(pha)006:356: de dag ni slob ma lhags par gnas pa'i cho ga'o //
NK014(pha)006:357: de ltar sa chog dang sta gon gyi rim pa rnams song nas /
NK014(pha)006:361: sgrub mchod rnams rje bla mas mdzad pa'i dkyil chog rdo rje'i phreng ba dang /
NK014(pha)006:362: sgrub thabs bde chen char 'bebs ltar bya'o //
NK014(pha)006:364: thog mar phan dbang gi dbang rdzas rnams chab gcig rab gnas byas na 'jug pa bde bas /
NK014(pha)006:366: h+aum big+h+n+aam ta kri ta phata /
NK014(pha)006:369: dbang rdzas rnams mi dmigs par stong pa nyid du gyur /
NK014(pha)006:370: stong pa'i ngang las pad zla nyi ma'i gdan la
NK014(pha)006:371: h+aum yig zung lnga 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa
NK014(pha)006:372: las so so'i phyag mtshan sa bon gyis mtshan par
NK014(pha)006:375: slar yang 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pas badz+ra he
NK014(pha)006:376: ru ka mthing nag rdo rje dang dung khrag 'dzin
NK014(pha)006:377: pa / bud+d+ha he ru ka smug nag 'khor lo dang dung khrag 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)006:378: rat+na he ru ka ser nag rin chen dang dung khrag 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)006:379: pad+ma he ru ka dmar nag pad+ma dang dung khrag 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)006:380: karma he ru ka ljang nag rgya gram dang dung khrag 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)006:381: thams cad kyang zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa rang rigs
NK014(pha)006:382: kyi yum dang mnyam par sbyor zhing zhabs gnyis g.yas
NK014(pha)006:383: brkyang ba'i dor stabs kyis bzhugs pa gar dgu'i ros
NK014(pha)006:384: sgeg cing dur khrod rol pa'i chas kyis brgyan pa
NK014(pha)006:385: / ye shes kyi me dpung 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa'o //
NK014(pha)006:386: sh+au nya t+aa sogs rang rigs bdag por byas pa'i sngags lnga tshan lngas bskur /
NK014(pha)006:387: k+aa ya badz+ra sogs kyis byin gyis brlab /
NK014(pha)006:391: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra gyis brtan par bya /
NK014(pha)006:392: kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod nas /
NK014(pha)006:393: yab yum mnyam par sbyor ba'i rjes chags kyis badz+ra
NK014(pha)006:394: he ru ka yab yum zhu ba las byung ba'i
NK014(pha)006:395: dbang rdzas gdugs dang rgyal mtshan dang g.yas pa'i cod
NK014(pha)006:396: pan / bud+d+ha he ru ka yab yum zhu ba las byung ba'i dbang rdzas bza' btung /
NK014(pha)006:397: rat+na he ru ka yab yum zhu ba las byung ba'i dbang rdzas dbu rgyan dang phreng ba /
NK014(pha)006:398: pad+ma he ru ka yab yum zhu ba las byung ba'i dbang rdzas g.yon pa'i cod pan /
NK014(pha)006:399: karma he ru ka yab yum zhu ba las byung ba'i dbang rdzas go cha /
NK014(pha)006:400: rigs lnga ka zhu ba las byung ba'i dbang rdzas snying po lnga dang bum pa rnams su gyur /
NK014(pha)006:401: phyag rgya lha'i dbang las 'phros pa'i chas dbang dang sgrub dbang gi rdzas lhag ma rnams bsang sbyangs /
NK014(pha)006:402: stong pa'i ngang las h+aum yig re re yongs su gyur pa las /
NK014(pha)006:403: sems nyid ye shes kyi rol pa ma 'gags pa'i
NK014(pha)006:404: cho 'phrul du rang snang ba khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i
NK014(pha)006:405: gdan dang phyag mtshan rgyan chas sgrub rdzas rnams rang
NK014(pha)006:406: rang gi rnam pa gsal la ma 'dres pas las
NK014(pha)006:407: dang dngos grub kyi mthu byin stsol ba la thogs
NK014(pha)006:408: pa med pa'i nus ldan du bsam pa'o //
NK014(pha)006:409: de nas cho ga dngos la /
NK014(pha)006:410: dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i cho ga dang /
NK014(pha)006:411: zhugs pa la mngon par dbang bskur ba'i cho ga gnyis /
NK014(pha)006:414: kun byas dbang phyug rig pas 'jug /
NK014(pha)006:415: de nas slob ma gzhug par bya //
NK014(pha)006:417: slob dpon 'jug pa'i chos gnyis dang /
NK014(pha)006:418: slob ma 'jug pa'i chos bcu dgu ste don nyer gcig yod pa las /
NK014(pha)006:419: dang po slob dpon 'jug pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:420: dkyil 'khor bzhengs sgrub kyi las rim kun tshar ba dang /
NK014(pha)006:421: slob dpon rang nyid slob ma 'jug pa ltar dkyil 'khor du zhugs te /
NK014(pha)006:422: dbang rnams bdag 'jug gi tshul du blang ba'am /
NK014(pha)006:423: mi nus na dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgor gus pas 'dug ste /
NK014(pha)006:424: rig pa'i me tog dor nas dngos grub bskul ba sgrub thabs ltar byas pas 'grub bo //
NK014(pha)006:425: gnyis pa slob ma gzhug par bzod gsol gnang ba zhi ba ni //
NK014(pha)006:426: rdo rje ye shes thob byed pa'i //
NK014(pha)006:427: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK014(pha)006:429: bdag gis slob ma gzhug par bya //
NK014(pha)006:431: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis slob bu dal du chug la /
NK014(pha)006:432: phan nus zab mo'i dbang gsum snod dang 'tshams par skur cig /
NK014(pha)006:433: ces gnang ba thob par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)006:434: gsum pa khrus bya ba ni /
NK014(pha)006:436: ji ltar bltams pa sogs kyis las bum gyi chus khrus byas nas /
NK014(pha)006:437: mtshams gcod srung 'khor sgom pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK014(pha)006:438: 'o nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad
NK014(pha)006:439: kyi don du bla na med pa yang dag par
NK014(pha)006:440: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas mi slob pa'i zung 'jug sku
NK014(pha)006:441: bzhi ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid chen po gang gi
NK014(pha)006:442: go 'phang tshe 'di nyid la mngon du bsgrub par
NK014(pha)006:443: bya / de'i ched du gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg
NK014(pha)006:444: pa'i lam gyi 'jug sgo dang po smin byed dbang
NK014(pha)006:445: gi rim pa rnams legs par nod nas lam zab
NK014(pha)006:446: mo bskyed rdzogs kyi rim pa gnyis la tshul bzhin
NK014(pha)006:447: du bslab par bagyi'o snyam pa'i byang chub mchog tu
NK014(pha)006:448: sems bskyed pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK014(pha)006:449: chos nyan pa'i kun tu spyod pa rnams kyang blang dor ma 'dzol bar bgyis te /
NK014(pha)006:451: de la gang zhig gsan par bya ba'i chos kyi
NK014(pha)006:452: rnam grangs kyang spyir bdag cag gi ston pa thabs
NK014(pha)006:453: la mkhas shing thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa
NK014(pha)006:454: de nyid kyis gdul bya'i sems can rnams kyi khams
NK014(pha)006:456: bsam pa'i rjes su 'gro ba'i chos kyi 'khor lo
NK014(pha)006:457: dpag tu med pa zhig bskor bar mdzad pa yin
NK014(pha)006:458: yang / re zhig spang gnyen gyi sgo nas bsdu na /
NK014(pha)006:459: gdul bya'i rgyud kyi nyon mongs pa'i bye brag brgyad
NK014(pha)006:460: khri bzhi stong gi gnyen por chos kyi phung po'ang
NK014(pha)006:461: de snyed cig tu grangs nges pa yin te /
NK014(pha)006:463: kun byed rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK014(pha)006:464: 'dod chags 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK014(pha)006:465: 'dul ba'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK014(pha)006:466: zhe sdang 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK014(pha)006:467: mdo sde'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK014(pha)006:468: gti mug 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK014(pha)006:469: mngon pa'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK014(pha)006:470: thams cad 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK014(pha)006:471: sde snod bzhi pa nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK014(pha)006:472: mdor na brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs pa kun //
NK014(pha)006:473: nyon mongs 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs par zad //
NK014(pha)006:475: de yang gzhung dang man ngag tsam gyi sgo nas bsdu na /
NK014(pha)006:476: gzhung mtshan nyid phar phyin gyi theg pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:477: man ngag gsang chen rdo rje'i theg pa gnyis su 'du ba yin te /
NK014(pha)006:479: theg pa rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK014(pha)006:480: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa dang //
NK014(pha)006:485: don gcig na yang ma rmongs dang //
NK014(pha)006:486: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK014(pha)006:487: dbang po rnon po'i dbang byas nas //
NK014(pha)006:488: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK014(pha)006:489: zhes bshad pa ltar khyad chos bzhi'i sgo nas khyad
NK014(pha)006:490: par du 'phags pa gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa
NK014(pha)006:491: nyid yin zhing / de la'ang shes byed rgyud sde'i
NK014(pha)006:492: rnam grangs bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig yod kyang
NK014(pha)006:493: lta spyod tsam gyi sgo nas bsdu na /
NK014(pha)006:494: spyod pa gtso bor ston pa bya ba'i rgyud dang /
NK014(pha)006:495: lta ba gtso bor ston pa rnal 'byor gyi rgyud
NK014(pha)006:496: de gnyis su gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde mtha' dag
NK014(pha)006:498: der yang rnal 'byor gyi rgyud tsam dang /
NK014(pha)006:499: rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i rgyud gnyis su yod pa las /
NK014(pha)006:500: 'di ni rnal 'byor bla na med pa la nang
NK014(pha)006:501: gses bskyed rdzogs rdzogs chen gsum ston pa'i gzhung rgyud
NK014(pha)006:502: lung man ngag gsum yod pa'i dang po rgyud ma
NK014(pha)006:503: h+aa yo ga / de la'ang bskyed rim thabs kyi
NK014(pha)006:504: cha dang rdzogs rim rlung gtso bor byed pas gsal
NK014(pha)006:505: stong rnam par mi rtog pa'i tshul gyis nyams su
NK014(pha)006:506: len pa ma h+aa'i ma h+aa ste pha rgyud gsang
NK014(pha)006:507: ba 'dus pa la sogs pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:508: bskyed rim gyi spros pa shas chung zhing shes rab
NK014(pha)006:509: rdzogs pa'i rim pa khams byang chub kyi sems thig
NK014(pha)006:510: le gtso bor byed pas bde stong rnam par mi
NK014(pha)006:511: rtog pa'i tshul du nyams su len pa ma h+aa'i
NK014(pha)006:512: a nu ste ma rgyud sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor dang
NK014(pha)006:513: dpal yang dag la sogs pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:514: bskyed rdzogs zung du 'jug cing de'ang rdzogs rim rtsa
NK014(pha)006:515: thig rlung gsum las bskyed pa'i bde gsal rnam par
NK014(pha)006:516: mi rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK014(pha)006:517: khyad par 'od gsal ye shes chen po la gtso
NK014(pha)006:518: bor byed pa'i tshul gyis nyams su len pa ma
NK014(pha)006:519: h+aa'i a ti ste gnyis med kyi rgyud sgyu 'phrul
NK014(pha)006:520: d+r+wa ba la sogs pa las /
NK014(pha)006:521: 'dir snga 'gyur bka' ma'i bka' srol rdo rje sems
NK014(pha)006:522: dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du
NK014(pha)006:523: dbang bskur ba skabs su babs pa yin /
NK014(pha)006:524: de la'ang thog mar nges shes 'dren pa bla ma brgyud pa'i lo rgyus kyi dbang du byas na /
NK014(pha)006:526: rgyal ba sems dpa' rnal 'byor pa //
NK014(pha)006:527: dgongs pa rig pa rna bar brgyud //
NK014(pha)006:528: ces gsungs pa ltar gsum las /
NK014(pha)006:529: dang po phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas thams cad
NK014(pha)006:530: kyi bdag nyid ston pa rigs drug pa bcom ldan
NK014(pha)006:533: 'chad pa'i skyes bu de bzhin gshegs pa lnga yang mngon par snang bar mdzad nas /
NK014(pha)006:534: rdo rje gsang ba la sogs pa rig pa khyad
NK014(pha)006:535: par can gyi 'khor rnams la rgyud kyi rgyal po
NK014(pha)006:536: nyid dgongs pa brda'i gsung gis /
NK014(pha)006:537: dus rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lor ston pa ni rgyal ba dgongs brgyud do //
NK014(pha)006:538: rgyal sras sems dpa'i 'khor rnams kyi nang nas rigs
NK014(pha)006:539: gsum mgon pos lha klu gnod sbyin gyi gnas su
NK014(pha)006:541: thub pa'i dbang po mya ngan las 'das nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad na /
NK014(pha)006:542: lang+ka'i yul te sing ga la'i gling gi ri bo
NK014(pha)006:543: ma la ya'am deng sang su ma na ku ta'i
NK014(pha)006:544: ri zhes grags pa'i rtse mor gsang bdag gis lha
NK014(pha)006:547: srin po blo gros thabs ldan /
NK014(pha)006:549: mi las skal ldan li tsa bi dri med grags pa ste /
NK014(pha)006:550: dam pa'i rigs can d+r+wa ma lnga la bshad pa rnams ni rig 'dzin brda brgyud do //
NK014(pha)006:551: de nas gang zag snyan brgyud ni /
NK014(pha)006:552: gsang bdag gis rigs can lnga la chos 'khor bskor
NK014(pha)006:553: ba'i byin rlabs kyis za hor gyi rgyal po dzahl
NK014(pha)006:554: rmi ltas ngo mtshar ba bdun rmis shing de'i rjes
NK014(pha)006:556: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK014(pha)006:557: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK014(pha)006:558: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yi //
NK014(pha)006:559: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK014(pha)006:560: 'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams kyi //
NK014(pha)006:561: rgyal po dzahzhesa bya ba la //
NK014(pha)006:562: bsod nams chen po'i mthus snang ba'i //
NK014(pha)006:563: gsang ba'i bdag pos snang bar 'gyur //
NK014(pha)006:564: zhes lung bstan pa ltar rgyal po nyid kyi pho
NK014(pha)006:565: brang gi khang thog tu tan+t+ra chen po sde bco
NK014(pha)006:566: brgyad kyi glegs bam char du babs shing /
NK014(pha)006:567: gsang ba'i bdag pos dngos su byin gyis brlabs nas don gyi brgyud pa gtad de /
NK014(pha)006:568: tshig gi brgyud pa li tsa bi nas len par
NK014(pha)006:569: rjes su gnang ba'i slar yang de nyid nas legs
NK014(pha)006:571: de ltar na gsang ba'i bdag po nas li tsa bi dri med grags pa /
NK014(pha)006:572: rgyal po dzah ku ku r+aa dzah in+d+ra b+hu ti /
NK014(pha)006:573: u pa r+aa dzah sras mo go ma de wi rnams la rim par brgyud de /
NK014(pha)006:574: thams cad tshogs kyi spyod pa'i nye rgyu la brten
NK014(pha)006:575: nas rang rang gi tshom bu dang bcas te rdo
NK014(pha)006:576: rje 'chang chen po'i sa la mngon du gshegs pa
NK014(pha)006:577: sha stag go // sras mos sgeg pa rdo rje dang slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba /
NK014(pha)006:578: de gnyis kas pan chen bi ma la mi tra /
NK014(pha)006:579: des bod du lo ts+aa ba rma gnyags gnyis /
NK014(pha)006:580: rma rin chen mchog nas mkhas pa gtsug gyer rnam gnyis /
NK014(pha)006:582: gnyags lo ye shes gzhon nu nas sog po dpal ye la brgyud de /
NK014(pha)006:583: zhang dang sog pos gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes la gnang /
NK014(pha)006:584: de nas gnubs yon tan rgya mtsho yab sras dang /
NK014(pha)006:585: chos lung gi nyang khu dbon nas lha rje zur po che sh+aakya 'byung gnas /
NK014(pha)006:586: de'ii slob ma rtse mo bzhi las lta sgom gyi rtse mo zur chung shes rab grags pa /
NK014(pha)006:587: de'i slob ma ka ba bzhi dang glan sh+aaka byang las /
NK014(pha)006:588: gsang bdag chen po sgro phug pa sh+aakya seng ge nas rim par brgyud de /
NK014(pha)006:589: kho bo cag gi bla ma dam pa bka' drin
NK014(pha)006:590: mnyam med 'dir rtsa ba'i bla ma'i mtshan smos te
NK014(pha)006:592: bdag rgyud dbang gi chu bos smin par mdzad pa yin /
NK014(pha)006:593: brgyud pa de las byung ba'i chos de la'ang /
NK014(pha)006:594: lam gyi gzhi smin byed dbang gi rim pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:595: de'i nyams len grol byed bskyed rdzogs kyi rim pa
NK014(pha)006:596: gnyis su yod pa las 'dir dbang bskur ba'i rim
NK014(pha)006:597: pa de skabs su bab pa yin /
NK014(pha)006:598: de la dbang gi ngo bo ni /
NK014(pha)006:599: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi tshogs pa la brten nas go 'phang gi chos rgyud la 'jog pa'i las kyis /
NK014(pha)006:600: rgyud kyi dri ma byang ba'am nyams smad par byas shing /
NK014(pha)006:601: thar pa'i myu gu mngon du skyes pa'am /
NK014(pha)006:602: skye nges kyi sa bon khyad par can gsos thebs
NK014(pha)006:603: pas lam bsgom rung dang 'bras bu thob rung gi
NK014(pha)006:604: nus pa mthu can du smin par byas pa ste
NK014(pha)006:605: / sa bon gsos thebs pa'i cha de sngags kyi sdom pa'ang yin la /
NK014(pha)006:608: a b+hi shiny+tsa'i sgra las drangs na /
NK014(pha)006:609: mngon par gtor bas na dbang ste /
NK014(pha)006:610: sbyang bya sgo gsum gyi dri ma gtor zhing 'khrud par byed pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)006:611: yang mngon par blugs pas na dbang ste /
NK014(pha)006:612: lam sgom rung dang 'bras bu thob rung gi nus pa khyad par can rgyud la 'jog pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)006:613: de ltar yang brtag gnyis las /
NK014(pha)006:614: gtor dang blugs pa zhes bya ba //
NK014(pha)006:615: des na dbang zhes brjod par bya //
NK014(pha)006:618: dad pa can rjes su 'dzin pa phan pa'i dbang nyer brgyad /
NK014(pha)006:619: brtson 'grus can rjes su 'dzin pa la nus pa'i dbang lnga /
NK014(pha)006:620: brtul zhugs can rjes su 'dzin pa la zab mo'i dbang gsum gsungs te /
NK014(pha)006:622: dad dang brtson 'grus brtul zhugs la //
NK014(pha)006:623: phan dang nus pa'i dbang bskur bya //
NK014(pha)006:624: shes rab dbang bskur rim par bcas //
NK014(pha)006:625: brtse bas chud mi za bar sbyin //
NK014(pha)006:627: de yang dbang bskur ba ni dkyil 'khor sngon du 'gro ba can yin la /
NK014(pha)006:628: de la'ang rdo rje rtse mo las /
NK014(pha)006:629: sems can shin tu gdul dka' gang //
NK014(pha)006:630: sdom pa 'dzin par mi byed cing //
NK014(pha)006:631: dad dang ldan pa med pa yang //
NK014(pha)006:632: 'jug pa nyid ni dgag mi bya //
NK014(pha)006:633: zhes pas re zhig dbang gi snod du ma gyur pa'i gang zag yin na'ang /
NK014(pha)006:634: dkyil 'khor du bcug pa tsam la 'gal ba med par gsungs mod /
NK014(pha)006:635: dkyil 'khor du ma bcug pa la dbang bskur ba ni nam du'ang mi rung ste /
NK014(pha)006:637: dkyil 'khor ma mthong ba rnams kyi mdun du ma smra zhig ces gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)006:639: kun byas dbang phyug rig pas 'jug /
NK014(pha)006:640: de nas slob ma gzhug par bya //
NK014(pha)006:641: zhes gsungs pa ltar sta gon du gnas pa yan chad song nas /
NK014(pha)006:643: rdo rje slob dpon gyi bya ba dang /
NK014(pha)006:644: rdo rje slob ma'i bya ba gnyis yod pa las /
NK014(pha)006:645: slob dpon gyi bgyi 'os dkyil 'khor bzhengs pa /
NK014(pha)006:647: bdag nyid dkyil 'khor du rig pas 'jug pa rnams chad lhag med par sngon du grub /
NK014(pha)006:648: da khyed rang slob ma rnams kyi ngo skal du gyur pa la /
NK014(pha)006:649: lha dang skal ba mnyam pa'i ched du dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i chos dang /
NK014(pha)006:650: zhugs nas dbang nod pa'i bya ba gnyis las /
NK014(pha)006:651: 'dir 'jug pa'i yan lag khrus dang bgegs bsal ba sngon du song nas /
NK014(pha)006:652: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo tha mi
NK014(pha)006:653: dad pa la dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i chos rnams
NK014(pha)006:654: zhu ba'i yon du man+dala phul mdzod /
NK014(pha)006:656: bzhi pa gdong dgab pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:657: dar ram ras dmar po'i mig dar /
NK014(pha)006:659: a kham w+ai ra h+aum gis me tog gtad /
NK014(pha)006:660: he ru ka dpal khyod la 'dud //
NK014(pha)006:661: thar lam chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK014(pha)006:662: de nyid dbang dang dam tshig dang //
NK014(pha)006:663: mgon po dpa' bor skyabs song ste //
NK014(pha)006:664: theg chen khang par gzhug pa dang //
NK014(pha)006:665: mkhyen rab ye shes bdag la stsol //
NK014(pha)006:666: lan gsum gyis gsol ba gdab /
NK014(pha)006:669: khyod kyi 'dod pa ji lta bu //
NK014(pha)006:671: drug pa lan gdab pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:673: skal ba bzang po thob par 'tshal //
NK014(pha)006:675: bdun pa drangs nas gral du dgod pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:676: lag gi rdo rje la 'jur bcug ste /
NK014(pha)006:677: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK014(pha)006:678: byang chub rdo rje'i lam nas drangs nas ni //
NK014(pha)006:679: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang dang dngos grub rnams //
NK014(pha)006:680: dwangs pa'i yid kyis rab tu blang bar gyis //
NK014(pha)006:681: zhes rim par drangs te dbang stegs pad+ma 'dab ma
NK014(pha)006:682: brgyad pa re bris pa'am bsgom pa'i steng du gral
NK014(pha)006:683: la bzhag / skabs 'dir dkyil 'khor gyi yol ba bsal /
NK014(pha)006:684: brgyad pa tshe sba ba ni /
NK014(pha)006:685: tshe mi yar bar bya ba'i phyir dbang phyug gi
NK014(pha)006:686: thugs ka'i sa bon las yi ge b+h+aum re slob
NK014(pha)006:688: b+h+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he zhes brjod pas dung khang
NK014(pha)006:689: zla gam dmar po'i gzhal yas khang gnam sgo gcig
NK014(pha)006:690: pa sgo khyud can gcig tu gyur /
NK014(pha)006:691: de'i nang du h+aum yig mthing skya dang /
NK014(pha)006:692: sgor h+aum yig ljang nag gcig gsal ba las 'od 'phros lus kyi nang gang /
NK014(pha)006:693: +aa yu h+aum dzah 'od zer tshur 'dus tshe bcud thams cad dbus kyi h+aum la thim pa las /
NK014(pha)006:694: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)006:695: ces brjod pas h+aum k+aa ra mthing skya rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams pa gcig tu gyur /
NK014(pha)006:696: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)006:697: ces pas sgo'i h+aum yig de mi g.yo ba ljang
NK014(pha)006:698: nag ral gri dang sdigs mdzub can gcig tu gyur
NK014(pha)006:699: te / srung ba'i las mdzad par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)006:700: dgu pa bgegs bskrad pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:701: slob dpon zhe sdang rdo rje'i snyems pas /
NK014(pha)006:702: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la phata phata phata /
NK014(pha)006:703: ha la ha la ha la h+aum /
NK014(pha)006:704: zhes brjod pas sprul pa'i khro tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa spros /
NK014(pha)006:705: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad gang /
NK014(pha)006:706: ltas chen po bco lnga dang /
NK014(pha)006:707: chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul chen pos bdud bgegs log
NK014(pha)006:708: par 'dren pa'i tshogs thams cad bsdigs bskrad brlag par
NK014(pha)006:709: bsam la / na mo dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)006:710: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:711: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:712: chos can rgyu 'bras bslu ba med pa'i bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:713: khyad par du'ang bcom ldan 'das sgyu 'phrul rnam par
NK014(pha)006:714: rol pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi bden
NK014(pha)006:715: pa dang / bden pa chen po'i byin gyi rlabs kyis /
NK014(pha)006:716: zhes bden stobs brjod pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK014(pha)006:717: 'dir 'dus pa'i slob bu rnams la gnod cing 'tshe
NK014(pha)006:718: ba'i 'byung po thams cad 'dir ma gnas par dengs
NK014(pha)006:720: h+aum bzhi pa'i sngags lan gsum brjod cing gu gul gyis bdug /
NK014(pha)006:722: slar yang khro bo rnams tshur 'dus phyogs mtshams thams
NK014(pha)006:723: cad khro bo dang rdo rje'i gur khang mtshon cha'i
NK014(pha)006:724: char 'bab cing / 'bar ba me'i phreng ba phyogs
NK014(pha)006:725: kun tu 'phro bas bcings te cis kyang mi shigs
NK014(pha)006:726: char 'bab cing / par bsam / bcu pa sgrib pa phral ba ni /
NK014(pha)006:727: slob dpon gyi lag pa g.yas kyi sor mo lnga
NK014(pha)006:728: la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor re re'i steng du h+aum
NK014(pha)006:729: s+w+aam +aam h+aam / g.yon gyi sor mo lnga la
NK014(pha)006:730: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor re re'i steng du m+aum l+aam
NK014(pha)006:731: m+aam p+aam t+aam rnams kyis mtshan par rigs lnga yab
NK014(pha)006:739: rigs lnga yab yum mnyam par sbyor bar bsam /
NK014(pha)006:740: gong ltar bden stobs brjod pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK014(pha)006:741: slob bu 'di rnams kyi rgyud la yod pa'i las kyi sgrib pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:742: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:744: lta ba dman pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:745: chos kyi phongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:746: bag chags ngan pa'i sgrib pa la sogs te sgrib
NK014(pha)006:747: pa'i phung po ji snyed pa thams cad phyag rgya'i
NK014(pha)006:750: zhes mang du brjod cing phyag rgya sprugs pas /
NK014(pha)006:751: rigs lnga'i sbyor mtshams nas byang chub sems kyi 'od
NK014(pha)006:752: zer 'phros pas slob bu'i sgrib pa mtha' dag bsregs
NK014(pha)006:753: shing sbyangs / dung khang gi khro bo gnyis kyang
NK014(pha)006:754: zhu lugs su thim pa'i rkyen gyis bu'i lus kyang
NK014(pha)006:755: 'od du zhu ba'i 'od phung gser zhun ma lta
NK014(pha)006:757: bcu gcig pa lhar bskyed pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:758: slob dpon gyi h+aum zhes brjod pas 'od phung de nyid h+aum yig mthing nag tu gyur /
NK014(pha)006:761: 'phro 'dus rdo rje rtse dgu par gyur /
NK014(pha)006:764: slar yang 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las he
NK014(pha)006:765: ru ka mthing nag rdo rje dang dung khrag can
NK014(pha)006:766: du gyur / bcu gnyis pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:767: so so'i phyag rgya slob ma'i mgo bo'i gnas lngar bzhag la /
NK014(pha)006:768: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra sogs /
NK014(pha)006:776: zhes brjod cing rdo rje gnas gsum du gtugs pas byin gyis brlab /
NK014(pha)006:777: slar yang rdo rje rtse lnga'i rgya bcings pa gnas gsum du bzhag la /
NK014(pha)006:778: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)006:779: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aa ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)006:780: sarba ta th+aa ga ra ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)006:781: zhes byin gyis brlabs pa'i rtags su gnas gsum du
NK014(pha)006:782: sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i lha rang rtags sa bon
NK014(pha)006:783: gyis mtshan pa 'dzin pas rgyas btab par bsam /
NK014(pha)006:784: bcu gsum pa go bgo ba ni /
NK014(pha)006:785: spyi bor ham bkod pa zhu ba lus thams cad rdo rje'i go chas bcings par bltas la /
NK014(pha)006:786: rdo rje go cha'i phyag rgya spyi bor 'ching zhing /
NK014(pha)006:787: badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi rak+sha ham /
NK014(pha)006:789: bcu bzhi pa lus bsrung ba ni /
NK014(pha)006:790: mdzub mo g.yas g.yon gnyis su dang trum las rdo
NK014(pha)006:791: rje gnod sbyin dang mi 'chi thabs sbyor bskyed la
NK014(pha)006:793: zhes lte ba snying ga ltag pa dpral ba spyi
NK014(pha)006:794: bo rnams su rim par mdzub mo gnyis bsnol ba
NK014(pha)006:795: reg pas / gnas de dang der khro bo gnyis
NK014(pha)006:796: po zhabs bsnol nas zhal phyir gzigs te bsrung ba'i
NK014(pha)006:797: las mdzad pa'i thugs ka nas rdo rje lu gu
NK014(pha)006:798: rgyud byung bas bsrungs shing brtan par bsam /
NK014(pha)006:799: bco lnga pa dam tshig dpog pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:800: thod pa'i bdud rtsi la sangs rgyas thams cad kyi
NK014(pha)006:801: rdo rje gsum gyi rang bzhin +aahh+aum gi rnam par
NK014(pha)006:804: dpal ldan rdo rje sku 'chang ba //
NK014(pha)006:805: mi phyed rdo rje gsum dang ldan //
NK014(pha)006:806: deng bdag sangs rgyas sku 'dzin pa //
NK014(pha)006:807: byin gyis brlab pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK014(pha)006:809: slob dpon gyis bdud rtsi las yig dkar po blangs par mos la /
NK014(pha)006:810: rdo rjes bdud rtsi blangs te zhes tshig de nyid brjod bzhin du slob bu'i lce thog tu sbyin /
NK014(pha)006:811: de las 'od zer dkar po 'phros de bzhin gshegs
NK014(pha)006:812: pa thams cad kyi sku'i byin rlabs bsdus nas slob
NK014(pha)006:813: ma'i dpral bar thim par bsam la /
NK014(pha)006:814: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)006:815: zhes byin gyis brlabs pas sku'i dam tshig thob par bsam /
NK014(pha)006:817: dpal ldan rdo rje'i gsung 'chang ba //
NK014(pha)006:818: mi phyed rdo rje gsum dang ldan //
NK014(pha)006:819: deng bdag sangs rgyas gsung 'dzin pa //
NK014(pha)006:820: byin gyis brlab pa'i gnas mdzod cig /
NK014(pha)006:822: slob dpon gyis bdud rtsi las +aahyiga dmar po blangs par mos te /
NK014(pha)006:824: de las 'od zer dmar po 'phros de bzhin gshegs
NK014(pha)006:825: pa thams cad kyi gsung gi byin rlabs bsdus nas
NK014(pha)006:826: slob ma'i mgrin par thim par bsam la /
NK014(pha)006:827: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aa ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)006:828: zhes byin gyis brlabs pas gsung gi dam tshig thob par bsam /
NK014(pha)006:830: dpal ldan rdo rje thugs 'chang ba //
NK014(pha)006:831: mi phyed rdo rje gsum dang ldan //
NK014(pha)006:832: deng bdag sangs rgyas thugs 'dzin pa //
NK014(pha)006:833: byin gyis brlab pa'i gnas mdzod cig /
NK014(pha)006:835: slob dpon gyis bdud rtsi las h+aum yig sngon po blangs par mos te /
NK014(pha)006:837: de las 'od zer mthing ga 'phros de bzhin gshegs
NK014(pha)006:838: pa thams cad kyi thugs kyi byin rlabs thams cad
NK014(pha)006:839: bsdus nas slob ma'i snying khar thim par bsam la
NK014(pha)006:840: / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)006:841: zhes byin gyis brlabs pas thugs kyi dam tshig thob par bsam /
NK014(pha)006:842: de nyid tshig gis dpog pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:843: mi ldog rigs nges brtan bya'i phyir //
NK014(pha)006:844: thar lam 'dren pa'i bla ma dang //
NK014(pha)006:845: byang chub 'gro ba'i spun rnams la //
NK014(pha)006:846: sgo gsum zol med bkur ba dang //
NK014(pha)006:847: gsang ba'i yid kyis bsrung bya zhing //
NK014(pha)006:848: he ru dpal la rtag gnas nas //
NK014(pha)006:849: mtha' yas sems can bu bzhin skyongs //
NK014(pha)006:851: bcu drug pa chu nan bya ba la /
NK014(pha)006:852: nyes dmigs kyi sgo nas chu nan bya ba dang /
NK014(pha)006:853: phan yon gyi sgo nas chu nan bya ba gnyis /
NK014(pha)006:855: tsan dan dkar dmar sbyar ba'i chu bsang sbyangs /
NK014(pha)006:856: stong pa'i ngang las h+aum las khro bo rdo rje gnod sbyin du gyur /
NK014(pha)006:858: zhes bzlas pas lha 'od du zhu ba chu'i rdul phra rab tu bsam la /
NK014(pha)006:859: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK014(pha)006:860: sdom pa las ni gang 'das pa //
NK014(pha)006:861: lha rnams dang ni mi rnams dang //
NK014(pha)006:862: sgrub pa po dang rnal 'byor rnams //
NK014(pha)006:863: de kun khros nas khrag chen po //
NK014(pha)006:864: nyams pa'i snying nas drangs te 'thung //
NK014(pha)006:865: i dam te na ra kan h+aum /
NK014(pha)006:866: zhes rdo rjes lce la lan gsum bzhag /
NK014(pha)006:868: slar yang chu de nyid bsang sbyangs /
NK014(pha)006:869: stong pa'i ngang las h+aum las rdo rje he ru ka'i skur gyur /
NK014(pha)006:870: badz+ra a mri tam a d+hi tish+tha mam h'u h+r+aihth+aah zhes bzlas pas /
NK014(pha)006:871: lha zhu ba las byung ba'i bdud rtsir bsam la /
NK014(pha)006:872: de lta bas na bu khyod kyis //
NK014(pha)006:873: dam tshig 'di dag bsrung bar gyis //
NK014(pha)006:874: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub pas //
NK014(pha)006:875: rdo rje bdud rtsi'i chu 'thung zhig /
NK014(pha)006:876: badz+ra u da ka h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)006:877: ces sngar ltar byin rjes 'di ltar brjod de /
NK014(pha)006:878: de ltar bdud rtsi'i chu de bzhag pa lce la bzhag kyang /
NK014(pha)006:879: bab pa snying gi dkyil du babs nas gal te dam tshig ma bsrung na /
NK014(pha)006:880: chu de rdo rje gnod sbyin zhes bya ba lcags
NK014(pha)006:881: kyi sdig pa mgo bo dgu par gyur nas snying
NK014(pha)006:882: khrag zho bzhin 'jib pas tshe thung zhing nad mang
NK014(pha)006:883: ba dang / tshe phyi mar dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal gyis nyam thag par 'gyur ro //
NK014(pha)006:884: dam tshig bsrung na chu de rdo rje sems dpar gyur nas des rtag tu byin gyis rlob cing /
NK014(pha)006:886: smon brgyad du gyur nas nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi gdon stong phrag brgyad cus mi tshugs pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:887: phyi mar bla na med pa'i byang chub thob nas
NK014(pha)006:888: sems can thams cad mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las
NK014(pha)006:889: 'das pa'i gnas su 'dren pa'i ded dpon byed par
NK014(pha)006:891: bcu bdun pa dam tshig bsgrag pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:892: bla ma'i phyag g.yas rdo rje dang bcas spyi bor bzhag la /
NK014(pha)006:893: rgyal bas gsungs pa'i ye shes gang //
NK014(pha)006:894: deng 'dir dngos grub mchog tu gsungs //
NK014(pha)006:895: dam tshig che ba'i chen po mchog /
NK014(pha)006:896: bye brag med par deng nas spyod //
NK014(pha)006:897: dge dang mi dge'i chos rnams la //
NK014(pha)006:898: lhag par brtan par mi bya ste //
NK014(pha)006:899: mnyam nyid rig pa'i klong zhugs nas //
NK014(pha)006:900: ci la'ang thogs pa med par spyod //
NK014(pha)006:902: bco brgyad pa rin chen dor ba ni /
NK014(pha)006:903: sngar gtad pa'i me tog thal sbyar gyis bzung la /
NK014(pha)006:905: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK014(pha)006:906: dur khrod rdzas kyi me tog dor nas kyang //
NK014(pha)006:907: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub rnams //
NK014(pha)006:908: skal ldan bdag cag rnams la stsal du gsol //
NK014(pha)006:909: pra t+aits+tsha badz+ra hoh zhes man+dala ra bar ltos med du dor /
NK014(pha)006:910: dbus su babs na rdo rje'i rigs /
NK014(pha)006:914: byang du las rigs te de ltar rigs gang yin ngos bzungs shig /
NK014(pha)006:916: pra t+ai gri h+na t+wam i mam sat+wa ma h+aa ba la tish+tha /
NK014(pha)006:918: bcu dgu pa lha dbab pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:919: slob bu rnams lus bde lugs su bsrangs te rlung rang babs su bzhag la /
NK014(pha)006:920: snying nang du chu nan gyi ye shes pa he
NK014(pha)006:921: ru ka mthing nag zhal phyag phyag mtshan yongs su
NK014(pha)006:922: rdzogs par gsal ba la shes pa skad cig kyang
NK014(pha)006:925: rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i rgya bcas la /
NK014(pha)006:926: badz+ra ma h+aa krod+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+he shwa r+ai sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)006:928: rdo rje sems dpa' chos sku las gzugs skur bzhengs par bsam la /
NK014(pha)006:929: dbang phyug gis lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang bcas /
NK014(pha)006:930: badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK014(pha)006:931: badz+ra kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai sa ma ya s+t+aam /
NK014(pha)006:932: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK014(pha)006:933: e h+ye hi +aa na ya dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes
NK014(pha)006:934: brjod pas 'og min nas ye shes sems dpa'i rang
NK014(pha)006:935: bzhin he ru ka'i sku che chung bsam gyis mi
NK014(pha)006:936: khyab pa byon nas slob ma'i spyi bo'i steng gi
NK014(pha)006:937: nam mkhar bzhugs par bsam la /
NK014(pha)006:938: 'phags mchog thugs rje'i dus la bab //
NK014(pha)006:939: khyad par bstan pa'i dus la bab //
NK014(pha)006:940: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK014(pha)006:941: byin gyis brlab pa'i dus la bab //
NK014(pha)006:942: dbang mchog skur ba'i dus la bab //
NK014(pha)006:943: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus la bab //
NK014(pha)006:945: byin chen byin phob bcom ldan 'das //
NK014(pha)006:946: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
NK014(pha)006:947: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK014(pha)006:948: bdag cag las 'bras mchis par mdzod //
NK014(pha)006:950: zhes brjod cing spos rol bya /
NK014(pha)006:951: de nas bla ma'i phyag g.yas rdo rje dang bcas pa slob ma'i snying gar bzhag la /
NK014(pha)006:953: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK014(pha)006:954: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi zad
NK014(pha)006:955: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:956: bden pa chen po'i byin gyi rlabs kyis byin phab
NK014(pha)006:957: pa'i ye shes pa de nyid tsit+ta'i dkyil du ye
NK014(pha)006:958: shes sems dpa'i rang bzhin du bzhugs nas 'jig rten
NK014(pha)006:959: 'di yi dge dgu dang smon brgyad du gyur te
NK014(pha)006:960: / phyi ma bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi rgyur gyur cig /
NK014(pha)006:961: gal te dam tshig nyams na rdo rje gnod sbyin
NK014(pha)006:962: du gyur te srog rtsa'i khrag 'jib par gyur cig
NK014(pha)006:965: ces pas snying gi sgo phye la nam mkha' gang
NK014(pha)006:966: ba'i lha tshogs rnams slob ma'i spyi bo nas zhugs
NK014(pha)006:967: pa snying ga'i he ru ka la sib sib thim
NK014(pha)006:968: par bsam zhing spos rol dang bcas te /
NK014(pha)006:970: zhes chu nan gyi lha dang gnyis med du gyur par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)006:971: skabs 'dir lha sgom pa'i thabs ston par gsungs kyang /
NK014(pha)006:972: 'og tu dal gyi lha ngo bstan pa dang sbrel nas mdzad pa phyag len no //
NK014(pha)006:973: nyi shu pa mig dbye ba ni /
NK014(pha)006:974: dbang phyug gi thugs ka nas 'od zer thur ma
NK014(pha)006:975: 'dra ba byung ste slob bu'i ma rig pa'i ling
NK014(pha)006:976: thog bsal bas dag pa ye shes kyi spyan dang
NK014(pha)006:978: de ring dad pa'i shugs kyis ni //
NK014(pha)006:980: sngags dang phyag rgya'i rigs su 'khrungs //
NK014(pha)006:981: khyod ni dam tshig 'di lta bu //
NK014(pha)006:982: gsang ba bstan pa'i snod du rung //
NK014(pha)006:983: dam tshig mchog tu 'gyur bar byed //
NK014(pha)006:984: dngos grub thams cad phun sum tshogs //
NK014(pha)006:985: badz+ra tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK014(pha)006:986: ces mig dbye zhing gdong g.yogs dkrol /
NK014(pha)006:987: nyer gcig pa dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:988: dbang phyug gis phyag shing thogs te /
NK014(pha)006:990: de yang srung ba'i 'khor los mi phyed par bcings
NK014(pha)006:991: pa'i nang dur khrod chen po brgyad kyis yongs su
NK014(pha)006:992: bskor ba'i dbus su sna tshogs pad+ma'i lte ba la
NK014(pha)006:993: rdzogs pa'i gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi 'khor
NK014(pha)006:995: ye shes rin po che'i rang bzhin b+hany+dza 'bar ba'i
NK014(pha)006:996: gzhal yas khang gi dbus ye shes lnga'i brdar 'khor
NK014(pha)006:997: lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa de'i phyir
NK014(pha)006:998: bden pa bzhi mtshon pa'i gru chad bzhis rnam par
NK014(pha)006:999: brgyan cing / che ba'i yon tan rgyas pas dbyibs gru bzhi pa /
NK014(pha)006:1000: rnam thar bzhi'i sgo nas 'jug pa'i sgo khyud can /
NK014(pha)006:1001: bden gnyis mtshon pa'i bar khyams rim pa gnyis kyi nang ma gser khyams dang /
NK014(pha)006:1002: phyi ma khrag khyams su gnas pa /
NK014(pha)006:1003: thod pa skam rlon rnyid gsum gyi rtsig pa phyi
NK014(pha)006:1004: ma ye shes lnga mtshon pa'i rim pa lnga dang
NK014(pha)006:1005: / nang ma rdo rje gsum mtshon pa'i rim pa gsum pa /
NK014(pha)006:1006: thams cad kyang rak+tasa spyin thabs su sbyar zhing gnam lcags kyi gzer bus btab pa /
NK014(pha)006:1007: rtsig steng thod pa sna tshogs kyi pha gu 'phyar ba las rgyu ma dang snying gi mgul 'khor /
NK014(pha)006:1008: bre phul gyi snam bur sbrul sbram dang thod phreng gi d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa /
NK014(pha)006:1011: rim pa gnyis ka'i rtsig pa'i 'gram du 'dod pa'i snam bu dang /
NK014(pha)006:1012: sgo phyi ma la rgyu 'bras kyi rta bab sogs 'jigs pa'i rgyan sna tshogs kyis bkra ba /
NK014(pha)006:1013: steng zhing lpags kyis thog phub nyi zla'i mthongs skar
NK014(pha)006:1014: dang bcas pa'i dbus phyur bu lha chen po'i thod
NK014(pha)006:1015: pas zlum por phub pa'i rtse mor tsit+ta'i tog gis
NK014(pha)006:1016: mtshan pa / de lta bu'i gzhal med khang gi nang na gdan gyi rim pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:1017: khrag 'thung rigs lnga'i gnas su pad zla nyi ma
NK014(pha)006:1018: brtsegs pa'i steng du dug lnga gnas su dag pa'i
NK014(pha)006:1019: brdar dbus su gtum pa dom /
NK014(pha)006:1024: byang du stag rnams zung zung gis sbar bas /
NK014(pha)006:1025: dbus su dbang phyug dang drag po /
NK014(pha)006:1029: byang du gnod sbyin rnams pho mo kha sbub gan
NK014(pha)006:1030: rkyal du bsnol ba'i sog dbrag dang nu dbrag nas
NK014(pha)006:1031: las la nan tur du 'dzud pa'i phyir bzung ba
NK014(pha)006:1032: / gnas yul sgo skyong rnams la nyi ma dang zhing gi gdan /
NK014(pha)006:1033: dbang mo rnams kyi gnas su zhing skam po'i gdan re re ste /
NK014(pha)006:1034: de rnams ni rten gyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK014(pha)006:1036: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus kyi gdan la zhe sdang dag
NK014(pha)006:1037: pa thugs rdo rje'i bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das dgyes
NK014(pha)006:1038: pa chen po badz+ra he ru ka sku mdog mthing
NK014(pha)006:1039: nag mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs
NK014(pha)006:1040: bzhi pa / zhal gdangs shing mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK014(pha)006:1041: ljags bsgril zhing rdo rje'i gad mos sa gsum g.yo ba /
NK014(pha)006:1042: khro gnyer bsdus pa'i shangs nas mi bzad pa'i h+aum
NK014(pha)006:1043: sgra 'byin cing rdzi smin sma ra las me 'bar
NK014(pha)006:1044: ba / zhal re re la dmar la zlum pa'i spyan gsum gsum dang ldan pa /
NK014(pha)006:1045: sku che zhing yan lag rags pa /
NK014(pha)006:1046: lang tsho rgyas pa'i 'gyur bag can rdo rje'i ba spus gtams pa /
NK014(pha)006:1047: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyis rdo rje rtse
NK014(pha)006:1048: dgu dang dril bu 'dzin pas yum la 'khyud pa
NK014(pha)006:1049: / bar pa gnyis kyis rdo rje rtse lnga dang dung dmar /
NK014(pha)006:1050: tha ma gnyis kyis zhing dbyug dang stong gi 'jig rten 'degs pa /
NK014(pha)006:1051: zhabs bzhi g.yas brkyang zhing g.yon bskum pa'i gyad chen po'i stabs kyis rol ba /
NK014(pha)006:1052: gar dgu'i nyams kyis sgeg cing dur khrod rol pa'i
NK014(pha)006:1053: chas brgyad dang dpal gyi chas bcu sku la rdzogs
NK014(pha)006:1054: pa / yum kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma sngo skya zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum pa /
NK014(pha)006:1055: dril bu dang dung dmar 'dzin cing khro mo'i cha
NK014(pha)006:1056: lugs rdzogs pas gtso bo dang dgyes par 'khril ba
NK014(pha)006:1057: stong nyid snying rje zung du 'jug pa'i bdag nyid
NK014(pha)006:1058: can me dpung 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa'o //
NK014(pha)006:1059: rtsibs bzhi'i shar du gti mug dag pa sku rdo rje'i bdag nyid bud+d+ha he ru ka yab yum /
NK014(pha)006:1060: lhor nga rgyal dag pa yon tan rdo rje'i bdag nyid rat+na he ru ka yab yum /
NK014(pha)006:1061: nub tu 'dod chags dag pa gsung rdo rje'i bdag nyid pad+ma he ru ka yab yum /
NK014(pha)006:1062: byang du phrag dog dag pa phrin las rdo rje'i bdag nyid karma he ru ka yab yum /
NK014(pha)006:1063: de'i phyi rol gyi rtsibs mchan dang gru chad bzhi
NK014(pha)006:1064: la rnam shes tshogs brgyad gnas su dag pa'i rtags
NK014(pha)006:1072: tsan+da l+ai ste gnas kyi ma mo brgyad /
NK014(pha)006:1073: gser khyams kyi phyogs bzhi dang mtshams bzhir yul brgyad gnas su dag pa'i rtags su /
NK014(pha)006:1077: spyang gdong ma ste mche ba can bzhi dang /
NK014(pha)006:1081: 'ug gdong ma ste gshog pa can bzhi ste yul gyi phra men brgyad /
NK014(pha)006:1082: dkyil 'khor nang ma'i sgo bzhir phyin ci log bzhi gnas su dag pa'i rtags su /
NK014(pha)006:1086: spyang gdong ma ste sgo ma bzhi /
NK014(pha)006:1087: dkyil 'khor phyi ma'i khyams dang sgo bzhir sgal tshigs nyer brgyad gnas su dag pa'i rtags su /
NK014(pha)006:1088: srin mo chen mo mi'i srin mo dang /
NK014(pha)006:1101: ra ro khrag 'thung myos ma dang /
NK014(pha)006:1113: ra mgo dmar ser chen mo dang /
NK014(pha)006:1114: bum sna sngo nag chen mo dang /
NK014(pha)006:1115: gsus 'dzin ser nag chen mo ste dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK014(pha)006:1117: phyi rol srung ba'i 'khor lo la khro bo chen
NK014(pha)006:1118: po yab yum zung bcu la sogs te sprul pa
NK014(pha)006:1119: dang yang sprul 'khor tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab pas
NK014(pha)006:1121: de ltar na sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba khrag 'thung lnga
NK014(pha)006:1122: bcu rtsa brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor chen po rten dang
NK014(pha)006:1123: brten par bcas pa thams cad mngon sum bzhin du
NK014(pha)006:1124: mjal bar gyur snyam du dga' ba dang spro ba
NK014(pha)006:1126: de'i nang nas kyang khyod kyi yi dam gyi lha ni 'di yin te /
NK014(pha)006:1127: de yang sngon me tog dbus su babs pa rnams
NK014(pha)006:1128: kyi yi dam gyi lha badz+ra he ru ka yiin
NK014(pha)006:1129: pa dang / snying po sngags ni /
NK014(pha)006:1130: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK014(pha)006:1131: sarba dush+tan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum
NK014(pha)006:1133: de bzhin shar du babs pa rnams kyi yi dam gyi lha ni bud+d+ha he ru ka dang /
NK014(pha)006:1135: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru
NK014(pha)006:1136: ka ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+tan+ta ka ha na da
NK014(pha)006:1137: ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)006:1139: lho ru babs pa rnams kyi yi dam gyi lha ni rat+na he ru ka dang /
NK014(pha)006:1141: rat+na ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK014(pha)006:1142: sarba dush+tan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum
NK014(pha)006:1144: nub tu babs pa rnams kyi yi dam gyi lha ni pad+ma he ru ka dang /
NK014(pha)006:1146: pad+ma ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK014(pha)006:1147: sarba dush+tan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum
NK014(pha)006:1149: byang du babs pa rnams kyi yi dam gyi lha ni karma he ru ka dang /
NK014(pha)006:1151: karma ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK014(pha)006:1152: sarba dush+tan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum
NK014(pha)006:1153: h+aum h+aum phata / ces pa ste /
NK014(pha)006:1154: de ltar na dus rtag tu lha de dang de'i
NK014(pha)006:1155: mngon rtogs sgom pa dang sngags bzla ba la brtson
NK014(pha)006:1157: de nas skabs 'dir rigs gang la babs pa'i gsang mtshan gdags par bya ste /
NK014(pha)006:1172: rdo rje bee ro tsa na rtsal /
NK014(pha)006:1178: rdo rje yon tan gter 'byung rtsal /
NK014(pha)006:1180: rdo rje rin chen snying po rtsal /
NK014(pha)006:1189: rdo rje ma chags pad+ma rtsal /
NK014(pha)006:1203: zhes pa lta bu rigs dang mthun pa'i ming gdags te /
NK014(pha)006:1204: de lta bu'i ming de nyid ma brjed par gyis shig /
NK014(pha)006:1205: ma 'ongs pa'i dus su rigs de dang der mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i tshe /
NK014(pha)006:1208: sa steng gsum du grags par 'gyur zhing sems can gyi don byed pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:1209: khyad par du zhe sdang can la sogs pa'i gdul bya 'dul bar 'gyur ro //
NK014(pha)006:1211: de nas khe nyen bshad pa'i sgo nas lha sgom par gdams pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:1212: skal ba mnyam pa'i ye shes de //
NK014(pha)006:1213: gnyer na nye bar 'byung ba yi //
NK014(pha)006:1214: ya mtshan chen po 'byung bar nges //
NK014(pha)006:1215: dad med nyams na phung bar 'gyur //
NK014(pha)006:1216: lha spangs dge spyad don med pas //
NK014(pha)006:1217: gang gis phyag rgya 'di spangs na //
NK014(pha)006:1218: nyon mongs ngan song gnas su skye //
NK014(pha)006:1220: bla med 'bras bu rgyun yang chad //
NK014(pha)006:1221: rigs chad nyid du ltung bar 'gyur //
NK014(pha)006:1222: bdag nyid lha dang mnyam sbyor bas //
NK014(pha)006:1224: gcig dang du ma yongs bral bas //
NK014(pha)006:1227: de ltar dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa la yon tan
NK014(pha)006:1228: dang ma zhugs pa la skyon ci yod ce na
NK014(pha)006:1230: 'jigs byed stangs dpyal gnyis sam lnga //
NK014(pha)006:1231: byas te dad ldan rab zhugs na //
NK014(pha)006:1232: 'og min chen por nyid zhugs dang //
NK014(pha)006:1234: gang dag dad med mi 'jug pa //
NK014(pha)006:1235: byang chub chen por dbul bar 'gyur //
NK014(pha)006:1237: de dag ni dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i cho ga'o //
NK014(pha)006:1238: gnyis pa zhugs pa la mngon par dbang bskur ba'i cho ga ni /
NK014(pha)006:1240: de nas zab mo'i dbang bskur ba'i //
NK014(pha)006:1241: sdom ni rgyu rkyen dgos ched dang //
NK014(pha)006:1242: gegs dang ngo bo rnam grangs dang //
NK014(pha)006:1243: bskur thabs skyon dang yon tan 'bras //
NK014(pha)006:1244: zhes gsungs pa ltar don tshan bcus ston cing /
NK014(pha)006:1245: khyad par dbang bskur thabs la /
NK014(pha)006:1246: sdom ni yon dang khri rtsig gsol //
NK014(pha)006:1247: dgongs gsol dbang rnams sbyin pa'o //
NK014(pha)006:1251: de nas rigs kyi bu mchog des //
NK014(pha)006:1252: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK014(pha)006:1253: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /
NK014(pha)006:1254: rab tu gces dang yid 'thad dbul //
NK014(pha)006:1256: lus dang longs spyod thams cad ltos med du phul
NK014(pha)006:1257: bar mos te man+dala sngon du 'gro bas thal mo
NK014(pha)006:1258: sbyar la / rang rgyud gdos pas bcings pa'i phung po 'di //
NK014(pha)006:1259: bdag med rgyal ba'i zhing du sbyar ba'i phyir //
NK014(pha)006:1260: lus srog rdzas kyi mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK014(pha)006:1261: bla med sman pa'i mchog la 'bul lags na //
NK014(pha)006:1262: gnyis su med pa'i tshul du dgongs nas su //
NK014(pha)006:1263: blang dor med pa'i tshul gyis bzhes su gsol //
NK014(pha)006:1264: a la la hoh zhes lus dbul /
NK014(pha)006:1265: de nas bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha la phyag btsal te gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:1266: dpal ldan sangs rgyas kun bdag nyid //
NK014(pha)006:1267: brtse bar dgongs te bdag la yang //
NK014(pha)006:1268: dbang bskur bdud rtsi chen po nyid //
NK014(pha)006:1269: de ring rab tu gsal bar mdzod //
NK014(pha)006:1272: sangs rgyas dag ni thams cad kyi //
NK014(pha)006:1273: gsang ba rdo rje gsum las byung //
NK014(pha)006:1274: khams gsum kun gyis phyag byas pa //
NK014(pha)006:1275: dbang bskur gnang ba chen po sbyin //
NK014(pha)006:1277: spos dang rol mor bcas pas ru lu bzla bzhin
NK014(pha)006:1278: du dkyil 'khor la bskor ba bya zhing dbang phyug
NK014(pha)006:1280: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK014(pha)006:1281: gzugs sku 'ja' tshon bzhin du so sor gsal //
NK014(pha)006:1282: thabs dang shes rab mchog la mnga' brnyes pa //
NK014(pha)006:1283: rigs lnga bde bar gshegs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)006:1285: gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK014(pha)006:1286: slob bu'i re ba bskang ba dang //
NK014(pha)006:1287: sems can don phyir bdag rtsom na //
NK014(pha)006:1288: bzod par mdzod de dgongs su gsol //
NK014(pha)006:1289: zhes dbang phyug gis lha la bzod par gsol la /
NK014(pha)006:1290: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah zhes rdo rje bsdu ba'i sngags rgyas /
NK014(pha)006:1291: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa thams cad
NK014(pha)006:1292: mdun gyi nam mkhar sprin phung gtibs pa bzhin du
NK014(pha)006:1293: sad nas bzhugs par mos la me tog dang bcas
NK014(pha)006:1296: hoh phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK014(pha)006:1297: bdag rdo rje slob dpon 'di zhes bya bas slob
NK014(pha)006:1298: bu 'di rnams la sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dbang bskur
NK014(pha)006:1299: bas / de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis bdag la mthu bstan du gsol /
NK014(pha)006:1302: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis //
NK014(pha)006:1304: rdo rje shugs kyis bsgral nas kyang //
NK014(pha)006:1305: byin rlabs dam pa nod par bya'o //
NK014(pha)006:1306: zhes brjod cing dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su 'dug par
NK014(pha)006:1307: mos la rang nyid dbang khri la 'dug par bya'o
NK014(pha)006:1308: // de nas dbang bskur ba'i las rim dngos ni /
NK014(pha)006:1310: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs na //
NK014(pha)006:1311: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang //
NK014(pha)006:1312: rim pa bzhin du sbyin par bya //
NK014(pha)006:1313: snying rjes chud ma zos par bzung //
NK014(pha)006:1315: slob ma dad pa can la phyi phan pa'i dbang nyer brgyad /
NK014(pha)006:1316: rang gzhan gyi don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la nang nus pa'i dbang lnga /
NK014(pha)006:1317: spyod rig mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs can la gsang ba
NK014(pha)006:1318: zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur ba'i rim pa dang gsum
NK014(pha)006:1319: / dang po phan dbang bskur ba la /
NK014(pha)006:1320: gdan dang lha dbang phyag mtshan dang //
NK014(pha)006:1321: chas bcu sgrub rdzas bco lnga ste //
NK014(pha)006:1322: phyi dbang nyer brgyad phan pa'i dbang //
NK014(pha)006:1324: dang po dregs pa gdan gyi dbang ni /
NK014(pha)006:1325: slob ma dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgo'i nang rol du
NK014(pha)006:1326: badz+ra he ru ka'i rnam pas 'khod pa'i rkang 'og
NK014(pha)006:1327: tu dbang stegs zil gnon dregs pa'i gdan bting bar
NK014(pha)006:1329: khyu mchog ma he gzig dang stag /
NK014(pha)006:1330: gtum pa dom dang nyi zla'i gdan //
NK014(pha)006:1331: zhabs bzhis bdud bzhi 'dul ba'i rtags //
NK014(pha)006:1332: dregs pa'i gdan gyi dbang bskur ro //
NK014(pha)006:1333: rak+sha yak+sha s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra man+da la a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK014(pha)006:1335: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK014(pha)006:1336: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi zad
NK014(pha)006:1337: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bden pa chen po'i byin
NK014(pha)006:1338: gyi rlabs kyis / skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la dregs pa'i gdan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK014(pha)006:1339: khams gsum gyi dregs pa can thams cad 'dul zhing
NK014(pha)006:1340: tshar bcad de chags sdang dang rnam rtog thams cad
NK014(pha)006:1341: zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK014(pha)006:1342: cig / gnyis pa phyag rgya lha'i dbang ni /
NK014(pha)006:1343: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams mar me gcig las
NK014(pha)006:1344: gnyis chad kyi tshul du byon te slob bu la
NK014(pha)006:1345: thim pas lha rang rang gi skur gyur par bsam
NK014(pha)006:1346: la / e ma nga ni rang byung ba'i //
NK014(pha)006:1347: dpal chen khro rgyal nyid kyi sku //
NK014(pha)006:1349: nga yis khyod kyi lag tu sbyin //
NK014(pha)006:1350: rdo rje 'di ni khyod kyis longs //
NK014(pha)006:1351: yum chen badz+ra khro mo'i rgyal //
NK014(pha)006:1352: brtson 'grus pha rol phyin ma'i dbang //
NK014(pha)006:1353: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK014(pha)006:1354: gzugs kyi mchod pas mnyes bya'i phyir //
NK014(pha)006:1355: nam mkha'i rgyal mo khyod la sbyin //
NK014(pha)006:1356: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK014(pha)006:1357: badz+ra kro d+he shwa r+ai a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK014(pha)006:1359: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK014(pha)006:1360: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi zad
NK014(pha)006:1361: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:1362: bden pa chen po'i byin gyi rlabs kyis /
NK014(pha)006:1363: skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la dpal chen
NK014(pha)006:1364: po badz+ra he ru ka yab yum gyi dbang bskur
NK014(pha)006:1365: bas / nyon mongs pa zhe sdang dang 'byung ba
NK014(pha)006:1366: nam mkhar 'dzin pa'i rtog pa gnas su dag nas
NK014(pha)006:1367: bas / / stong pa nyid kyi ye shes su lhun gyis grub ste /
NK014(pha)006:1368: nyon mongs pa zhe sdang gi mtha' la gnas pa
NK014(pha)006:1369: rnams dus gcig la sgrol ba'i dbang dam pa thob
NK014(pha)006:1370: par gyur cig / e ma nga ni rang byung ba'i //
NK014(pha)006:1371: dpal chen khro rgyal nyid kyi sku //
NK014(pha)006:1373: nga yis khyod kyi lag tu sbyin //
NK014(pha)006:1375: yum chen bud+d+ha khro mo'i rgyal //
NK014(pha)006:1376: shes rab pha rol phyin ma'i dbang //
NK014(pha)006:1377: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK014(pha)006:1378: rol pa'i mchod pas mnyes bya'i phyir //
NK014(pha)006:1379: sra brtan rgyal mo khyod la sbyin //
NK014(pha)006:1380: bud+d+ha kro d+ha ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK014(pha)006:1381: bud+d+ha kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK014(pha)006:1383: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK014(pha)006:1384: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi zad
NK014(pha)006:1385: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)006:1386: bden pa chen po'i byin gyi rlabs kyis /
NK014(pha)006:1387: skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la dpal chen
NK014(pha)006:1388: po bud+d+ha he ru ka yab yum gyi dbang bskur
NK014(pha)006:1389: bas / nyon mongs pa gti mug dang 'byung ba sar 'dzin pa'i rtog pa gnas su dag nas /
NK014(pha)006:1390: me long lta bu'i ye shes su lhun gyis grub ste /
NK014(pha)006:1391: nyon mongs pa gti mug gi mtha' la gnas pa
