NK014(pha)006:2995: kyi kha dog can zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa rang
NK014(pha)006:2996: rtags dang dung khrag 'dzin pa dur khrod rol pa'i
NK014(pha)006:2997: chas brgyad kyis brgyan cing dpal gyi chas bcu rdzogs
NK014(pha)006:2998: pa sgeg pa la sogs pa gar dgu'i nyams can
NK014(pha)006:2999: zhabs g.yas brkyang ba'i dor stabs kyis rang 'dra'i yum
NK014(pha)006:3002: spyi gtsug tu h+aum mdzad sngo skya rang rtags mda' gzhu /
NK014(pha)006:3003: snying gar rnam rgyal dkar po kha t+w+aam ka dang tri shul /
NK014(pha)006:3004: nu ma g.yas su dbyug pa sngon po dbyug pa dang me dpung /
NK014(pha)006:3005: dpung mgo g.yas par gshin rje gshed mthing ga be con dang dgra s+t+wa /
NK014(pha)006:3006: sog steng g.yas par mi g.yo ba ljang dmar spu gri dang zhags pa /
NK014(pha)006:3007: sog dbrag tu rta mgrin dmar po ral gri dang sbrul zhags /
NK014(pha)006:3008: sog steng g.yon par gzhan gyis mi thub pa sngon po b+hany+dza dang rnga yab /
NK014(pha)006:3009: dpung mgo g.yon par bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang gu rgya gram dang dril bu /
NK014(pha)006:3010: nu ma g.yon du khams gsum rnam rgyal ser po 'khor lo dang mche ba /
NK014(pha)006:3011: gshang khar stobs po che dud kha tho ba dang gtun shing /
NK014(pha)006:3012: thams cad kyang zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang po gnyis rdo rje dung dmar /
NK014(pha)006:3014: tha ma gnyis phur bu 'dril ba //
NK014(pha)006:3015: zhabs bzhi dor stabs bgrad pa /
NK014(pha)006:3016: gar dgu'i nyams kyis sgeg cing dur khrod rol pa'i chas can /
NK014(pha)006:3017: rang 'od kyi yum yab kyi mdog can g.yas 'khyud
NK014(pha)006:3018: stabs dang g.yon dung dmar yab la stob pa khro
NK014(pha)006:3020: gtso 'khor thams cad kyang ye shes kyi me dpung 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa'o //
NK014(pha)006:3021: dbang rdzas rdor dril bsang sbyangs /
NK014(pha)006:3022: dbang rdzas mi dmigs par stong pa nyid du gyur /
NK014(pha)006:3023: stong pa'i ngang las pad zla nyi ma'i gdan la
NK014(pha)006:3024: h+aum zung las rdor dril sa bon gyis mtshan pa
NK014(pha)006:3025: 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las rigs 'dus badz+ra
NK014(pha)006:3026: he ru ka yab yum du gyur /
NK014(pha)006:3027: dkyil 'khor cha lnga khro bcu dang bcas pa dang dbang rdzas kyi lha la lnga tshan lngas bskur /
NK014(pha)006:3034: slob dpon gyi sbyor mtshams nas spros pa'i 'od kyis
NK014(pha)006:3035: bskul bas lha thams cad yab yum mnyam par sbyor
NK014(pha)006:3036: ba'i rjes chags kyis lus dkyil gyi lha tshogs rten
NK014(pha)006:3037: dang brten par bcas pa 'od du zhu ba slob
NK014(pha)006:3038: bur thim pa'i rkyen gyis slob ma yang 'od du
NK014(pha)006:3039: zhu ba'i 'od phung mthing ga las rigs 'dus badz+ra
NK014(pha)006:3041: dbang rdzas kyi lha 'od du zhu ba las rdo rje dang dril bur gyur /
NK014(pha)006:3042: de lta bu'i rdo dril lag tu gtad de snying
NK014(pha)006:3043: gar bsnol du bcug pa yan lag lnga'i reg shes
NK014(pha)006:3044: kyii thig le la thim par mos la //
NK014(pha)006:3045: phyogs bcu dus bzhi thams cad kyi //
NK014(pha)006:3046: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje che //
NK014(pha)006:3047: dkyil 'khor kun gyi byed pa po //
NK014(pha)006:3048: dkyil 'khor kun gyi sbyiin pa spyod //
NK014(pha)006:3049: de ltar rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang bskur bas deng
NK014(pha)006:3050: phyin chad bdag gzhan gyi don thams cad sgrub pa
NK014(pha)006:3051: la dbang thob par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)006:3054: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK014(pha)006:3055: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi zad
NK014(pha)006:3056: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bden pa chen po'i byin
NK014(pha)006:3057: gyi rlabs kyis / skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa
NK014(pha)006:3058: khyod la rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi
NK014(pha)006:3059: dbang bskur bas rdo rje rgyal po'i sa 'dzin cing
NK014(pha)006:3060: gyi rlabs kyis / / dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi
NK014(pha)006:3061: byed pa po'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK014(pha)006:3062: gyi rlabs kyis / / / de ltar nang lus
NK014(pha)006:3063: kyi dkyil 'khor du nus pa'i dbang lnga bskur bas
NK014(pha)006:3064: rang gzhan gyi don dngos su byed pa la dbang
NK014(pha)006:3065: gyi rlabs kyis / / / zhing / khyad par
NK014(pha)006:3066: gyi bskyed rim dang rdzogs rim rjes mthun pa rnams
NK014(pha)006:3067: nyan sgom 'chad par nus pa'i skal ba can du
NK014(pha)006:3069: gsum pa spyod rig mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs can la
NK014(pha)006:3070: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur ba la gsum
NK014(pha)006:3071: las / dang po gsang dbang la /
NK014(pha)006:3075: go ma yes khyem med par byugs pa'i stegs bu
NK014(pha)006:3076: tshad ldan la yum gyi mkha' dkyil mtshon byed pad+ma
NK014(pha)006:3077: dmar po 'dab ma bzhi pa sor bzhi pa'i tshad
NK014(pha)006:3078: can dang / thabs kyi gsang ba'i nor bu mtshon
NK014(pha)006:3079: byed rdo rje sngon po rtse lnga mdzub gang ba'i
NK014(pha)006:3080: tshad can so so'i mtshan ma dang bcas pa dag
NK014(pha)006:3081: can dang / bya'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:3083: he ru ka dpal khyod la 'dud //
NK014(pha)006:3084: thar lam chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK014(pha)006:3085: de nyid dbang dang dam tshig dang //
NK014(pha)006:3086: mgon po dpa' bor skyabs song ste //
NK014(pha)006:3087: theg chen khang par gzhug pa dang //
NK014(pha)006:3088: mkhyen rab ye shes bdag la stsol //
NK014(pha)006:3089: zhes lan gsum gyis gsol ba gdab /
NK014(pha)006:3091: bu 'dir shog cig ci bde bar //
NK014(pha)006:3092: las spyod riim par 'gro ba dang //
NK014(pha)006:3093: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje bzung //
NK014(pha)006:3094: rdzogs pa'i ye shes bde chen la //
NK014(pha)006:3095: dmigs pa med par gnas phyir du //
NK014(pha)006:3096: ser sna spangs pa'i dang yid kyis //
NK014(pha)006:3097: gtong zhing rang sems brtan por bzung //
NK014(pha)006:3098: ye shes rang gnas rdzogs dbang sbyin //
NK014(pha)006:3100: de nas slob dpon dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo bcom
NK014(pha)006:3101: ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po badz+ra he ru kar
NK014(pha)006:3102: gsal ba'i gnas lngar khrag 'thung rigs lnga dang /
NK014(pha)006:3103: lag pa g.yas g.yon kha dang gsang ba'i phyi rnams su khro bo bzhi /
NK014(pha)006:3104: phyag rgya lo nyi shu ma yum badz+ra kro d+he
NK014(pha)006:3105: shwa r+ai mar gsal ba'i gnas lngar rigs kyi yum
NK014(pha)006:3106: lnga dang / yan lag bzhi la khro mo bzhi rnams gsal bar gyur /
NK014(pha)006:3114: yab kyi gsang gnas h+aum las ye shes kyi rdo
NK014(pha)006:3115: rje rtse lnga pa'i lte bar byang chub kyi sems
NK014(pha)006:3116: dkar por gnas pa'i bu gar phata kyis bkag cing
NK014(pha)006:3117: rwa lnga la nyi ma la gnas pa'i dpa' bo
NK014(pha)006:3118: 'bru lnga / yum gyi mkha' pam las pad+ma dmar
NK014(pha)006:3119: po 'dab ma bzhi pa'i lte bar nyi ma la
NK014(pha)006:3120: rak+ta +aam dmar por gnas pa'i ge sar la a
NK014(pha)006:3121: 'bru lnga / / dbus dang 'dab bzhir zla ba
NK014(pha)006:3122: la gnas pa'i dpa' mo 'bru lngas mtshan par bsam
NK014(pha)006:3123: 'bru lnga / / la / sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)006:3124: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa go ham /
NK014(pha)006:3125: a nu r+aa ga ya mye /
NK014(pha)006:3126: zhes sbyor ba'i brdas phan tshun bsnol mar bskur te /
NK014(pha)006:3127: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes phyag rgya bzhis 'khyud sdom sprad
NK014(pha)006:3128: nas snyoms par zhugs pas byang chub kyi sems 'khor
NK014(pha)006:3129: lo bzhir dga' bzhi'i 'gros kyis phyin pa yab kyi
NK014(pha)006:3130: gsang ba rdo rje'i lam nas yum gyi pad+ma'i sna
NK014(pha)006:3131: rtse la khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad kyi dkyil
NK014(pha)006:3132: 'khor gsal ba la mchod par phul te /
NK014(pha)006:3133: yum mkhar bskyil ba'i yab yum gyi nyi zla byang chub kyi sems gnyis 'dres /
NK014(pha)006:3134: de nyid slob bu'i lce thog tu bzhag par mos la /
NK014(pha)006:3136: nga ni rgyal ba kun gyi bla //
NK014(pha)006:3137: thig le byang chub sems chen po //
NK014(pha)006:3138: nga ni khro rgyal kun gyi rje //
NK014(pha)006:3139: ye shes rol pa'i 'byung gnas gter //
NK014(pha)006:3140: nga ni spyi dpal bla na med //
NK014(pha)006:3141: skyon bral thabs kyi rgyal po yin //
NK014(pha)006:3142: sems kyi dkyil nas drangs pa'i chu //
NK014(pha)006:3143: khyod kyi lce la phab pa 'di //
NK014(pha)006:3144: snying gi dkyil du bzung bar byos //
NK014(pha)006:3145: rigs kyi bu mchog deng phan chad //
NK014(pha)006:3146: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs mchog bzung //
NK014(pha)006:3147: sangs rgyas kun gyi gtso bo yin //
NK014(pha)006:3148: byang chub sems dang mnyam pa'i phyir //
NK014(pha)006:3149: sems dpa' kun gyi mchog gnas yin //
NK014(pha)006:3150: rigs kyi bu mchog deng phan chad //
NK014(pha)006:3151: phyi dang nang dang gsang ba yi //
NK014(pha)006:3152: bstan pa phyi dang zab mo kun //
NK014(pha)006:3153: sems kyi dkyil du bsdus nas kyang //
NK014(pha)006:3154: rdo rje lce yi sgo phye ste //
NK014(pha)006:3155: bdud rtsi sman mchog dam pa 'dis //
NK014(pha)006:3156: dad ldan skyes bu ngoms par byos //
NK014(pha)006:3157: sems kyi thig le'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK014(pha)006:3158: zhi khro 'bar ba'i sku sgom la //
NK014(pha)006:3159: srid pa gsum la dbang sgyur cig /
NK014(pha)006:3160: dbang can thams cad bkol bar byos //
NK014(pha)006:3161: skye 'gro kun la snying brtse yis //
NK014(pha)006:3162: gdul ba'i phyag rgya 'di yang spyod //
NK014(pha)006:3163: dug gsum rtsa ba gcod par byed //
NK014(pha)006:3164: phyi nang snod bcud rnam par dag /
NK014(pha)006:3165: rnam dag chen po nyid kyi lam //
NK014(pha)006:3166: byed spyod thams cad tshogs gnyis rdzogs //
NK014(pha)006:3168: sems kyi chu 'di btung bar byos //
NK014(pha)006:3169: rnal 'byor chen po'i dam du bzung //
NK014(pha)006:3170: yungs kar tshad tsam rdo rje sems //
NK014(pha)006:3171: gnas ngan len pa gsum sbyangs te //
NK014(pha)006:3172: h+aum nyid ring pos mtshams sbyar te //
NK014(pha)006:3174: thams cad bde ba chen po'i dbyings //
NK014(pha)006:3175: dge sdig las kyis ma bcos shing //
NK014(pha)006:3176: bsgoms shing bsgrubs pas mi 'byung ba'i //
NK014(pha)006:3177: rnam dag sems kyi rin chen gter //
NK014(pha)006:3178: rdo rje snying po ye shes kyis //
NK014(pha)006:3179: khro rgyal kun gyi gtsor gyur cig /
NK014(pha)006:3180: sh+r+ai ma h+aa su kha badz+ra bo d+hi h+aum ho /
NK014(pha)006:3183: lce thog tu bzhag pa'i byang sems h+aum gi rnam
NK014(pha)006:3184: par gsal ba de nyid yungs 'bru tsam gyi rdo
NK014(pha)006:3185: rje sems dpa' sha stag tu gyur pa snying gar
NK014(pha)006:3186: thim pas chos kyi 'khor lo'i rtsa chen bzhi la
NK014(pha)006:3187: gnas pa'i rigs drug gi sa bon bag chags dang
NK014(pha)006:3188: bcas pa sbyangs nas sems nyid rnam par mi rtog
NK014(pha)006:3189: pa'i rang bzhin don spros med bde ba chen po'i
NK014(pha)006:3190: ye shes rgyud la skyes par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)006:3193: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK014(pha)006:3194: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi zad
NK014(pha)006:3195: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bden pa chen po'i byin
NK014(pha)006:3196: gyi rlabs kyis / skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa
NK014(pha)006:3197: khyod la gsang ba byang chub sems kyii da bang
NK014(pha)006:3198: bskur bas gnas ngan len pa'i sa bon bag chags
NK014(pha)006:3199: dang bcas pa dag nas gnas lugs don dam skye
NK014(pha)006:3200: med kyi ye shes mngon du rtogs pa'i dbang dam
NK014(pha)006:3202: de nas slar yang slob ma'i shes pa h+aum yig shel ltar dwangs pa yongs su gyur pa las /
NK014(pha)006:3203: skad cig gis che mchog he ru ka mthing nag rdo rje dang thod khrag bsnams pa /
NK014(pha)006:3204: de'i thugs kar gu h+ya he ru ka sngon po rdor dril /
NK014(pha)006:3205: de'i thugs kar sa nu he ru ka dkar po
NK014(pha)006:3206: phyag gnyis rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i phyag rgya can
NK014(pha)006:3207: gsal btab ste rdo rje dang dril bu lhan cig
NK014(pha)006:3208: snying gar bzung la bden pa brjod pa ni //
NK014(pha)006:3209: mi 'gyur ba yi ye shes gnas //
NK014(pha)006:3210: ma btsal phyin pas bde ba'i mchog /
NK014(pha)006:3211: ma bltas gsal ba'i ye shes spyan //
NK014(pha)006:3212: gong na med pas kun gyi rje //
NK014(pha)006:3213: ye shes rang gnas brdal ba la //
NK014(pha)006:3214: mi 'gyur g.yung drung sa thob shog /
NK014(pha)006:3215: ma h+aa gu h+ya b+h+r+aum dz+ny+aa na man+dala dz+ny+aa na gu h+ya sid+d+hi swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)006:3217: de nyid nus pa can du bya ba'i phyir ka
NK014(pha)006:3218: p+aa la'i dbu rgyan dang zhing gi cod pan mthing
NK014(pha)006:3220: de yang dbu rgyan bskon la /
NK014(pha)006:3222: thabs mkhas thugs rje byin rlabs kyis //
NK014(pha)006:3223: rigs kyi bu mchog dbang bskur phyir //
NK014(pha)006:3224: gsang ba'i dbu rgyan 'di bcings pas //
NK014(pha)006:3225: rigs kyi bu mchog deng phan chad //

NK014(pha)006:3228: sangs rgyas che ba mchod nas ni //
NK014(pha)006:3229: rnal 'byor chen po khyod nyid yin //

NK014(pha)006:3234: khyung gi gshog pa g.yas g.yon gdengs pa yis //
NK014(pha)006:3235: klu rnams zil gyis gnon par byed pa ltar //
NK014(pha)006:3236: srid gsum yon tan mchog tu rdzogs pa yi //
NK014(pha)006:3237: sangs rgyas kun la mdzes pa'i cod pan mchog /
NK014(pha)006:3238: mchog tu che bas bdud bzhi zil gyis gnon //
NK014(pha)006:3239: ta th+aa ga to ma h+aa gu h+ya badz+ra m+aa
NK014(pha)006:3240: la a b+hi shiny+tsa hoh de nas dbugs dbyung ba
NK014(pha)006:3241: ni / bu khyod mtshan ma'i rtog bral zhing //
NK014(pha)006:3242: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK014(pha)006:3243: kun la spyod pa'i dbang thob nas //
NK014(pha)006:3244: slob ma bde la 'god byed pa'i //
NK014(pha)006:3245: dbang phyug chen por deng gyur to //
NK014(pha)006:3247: gsang ba gnyer gtad pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:3248: gsang ba'i don mchog 'di dag ni //
NK014(pha)006:3249: lta ba dman la bstan byas na //
NK014(pha)006:3250: dus min par ni srog zad nas //
NK014(pha)006:3252: khab len gyis ni lcags sdud ltar //
NK014(pha)006:3253: mi 'dod bzhin du dbang med par //
NK014(pha)006:3254: bskal par ngan song myong bar 'gyur //
NK014(pha)006:3255: de bas shin tu gsang bar bya //
NK014(pha)006:3257: gnyis pa ye shes rang gnas sam shes rab ye shes kyi dbang ni /
NK014(pha)006:3258: man+dala sngon du 'gro bas bla ma la phyag rgya
NK014(pha)006:3259: mtshan ldan lo bcu drug ma rgyud dag par byas
NK014(pha)006:3261: he ru ka dpal khyod la 'dud //
NK014(pha)006:3262: thar lam chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK014(pha)006:3263: de nyid dbang dang dam tshig dang //

NK014(pha)006:3278: gung mo g.yon pa lto sbyar te rat+na'i phreng bas
NK014(pha)006:3279: bcings pa'i rtse nas dbang phyug gi mtheb srin gyiis
NK014(pha)006:3280: bzung ste slob ma la gtad par mos la /
NK014(pha)006:3281: bde ba chen po chos kyi sku //
NK014(pha)006:3282: shes rab thabs kyis rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK014(pha)006:3283: 'di dang skye ba thams cad du //
NK014(pha)006:3284: dngos grub bde 'di ma spongs shig /
NK014(pha)006:3285: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK014(pha)006:3286: rdzogs pa'i phyag rgya khyod las byung //
NK014(pha)006:3287: spangs nas rdo rje dbyings phyug rtsa //
NK014(pha)006:3288: dgug dang bsdam pa ma shes na //
NK014(pha)006:3289: rdo rje bskal pa mtha' klas par //
NK014(pha)006:3290: chos sku thob par mi 'gyur ro //
NK014(pha)006:3292: de nas slob ma dang gtad pa'i phyag rgya gnyis
NK014(pha)006:3293: phan tshun 'dod pa'i bstan bcos kyis bde ba rgyas
NK014(pha)006:3294: par byas rjes / slob ma dkyil 'khor gyi gtso
NK014(pha)006:3295: bo bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po badz+ra he
NK014(pha)006:3296: ru kar gsal ba'i gnas lngar khrag 'thung rigs lnga
NK014(pha)006:3297: par byas rjes / dang / lag pa g.yas g.yon
NK014(pha)006:3298: kha dang gsang ba'i phyi rnams su khro bo bzhi
NK014(pha)006:3299: par byas rjes / dang / / phyag rgya yum
NK014(pha)006:3300: badz+ra kro d+he shwa r+ai mar gsal ba'i gnas lngar
NK014(pha)006:3302: yan lag bzhi la khro mo bzhi rnams gsal bar gyur /

NK014(pha)006:3319: bo 'bru lnga / e / par bsam la / sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)006:3320: sa ma hoh a nu r+aa go ham /
NK014(pha)006:3321: a nu r+aa ga ya mye /
NK014(pha)006:3322: zhes sbyor ba'i brdas phan tshun bsnol mar bskul te /
NK014(pha)006:3323: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes phyag rgya bzhis 'khyud sdom sprad
NK014(pha)006:3324: nas snyoms par zhugs pas rjes chags kyi rlung bskyod
NK014(pha)006:3325: pas gtum mo 'bar ba'i rkyen gyis byang chub kyi
NK014(pha)006:3326: sems zhu ba la brten nas rtsa gnas thams cad
NK014(pha)006:3327: nas thig le g.yos pas bde ba 'go ldang ba'i
NK014(pha)006:3328: tshul du skyes pa g.yo ldang byang chub kyi sems
NK014(pha)006:3329: dang / bde ba phyi ma 'jug pa'i tshe snga
NK014(pha)006:3330: ma 'jig cing mthar thams cad 'gag pa 'jig 'jug
NK014(pha)006:3332: rten can gyi bde ba rang sa na gnas pa
NK014(pha)006:3333: med pa'i tshul gyis thams cad gnas pa gnas pa
NK014(pha)006:3335: snga ma'i bde bas mtshon nas phyi ma'i bde ba
NK014(pha)006:3336: thams cad la dmigs shing 'dun pa smon pa byang
NK014(pha)006:3338: de ltar gnas bzhir dga' bzhi'i 'gros kyis song ba'i
NK014(pha)006:3339: yab yum gyi rtsa thams cad kyi bcud 'dus pa'i
NK014(pha)006:3340: snying po nyi zla'i dwangs ma mkha' gsang rdo rje
NK014(pha)006:3341: dang pad+ma'i rtser 'phrad de zhal mjal ba las thabs
NK014(pha)006:3342: nyid shes rab tu sbyor ba /
NK014(pha)006:3343: shes rab thabs su sbyor ba /
NK014(pha)006:3344: thabs shes gnyis med du sbyor ba ste /
NK014(pha)006:3345: sbyor ba gsum gyi sgo nas dngos po lhan cig
NK014(pha)006:3346: skyes pa'i dga' ba nyams su myong ba mthar phyin
NK014(pha)006:3347: pa byang chub kyi sems te /
NK014(pha)006:3348: de ltar sems lnga'i rim pas yas babs bde ba
NK014(pha)006:3349: chen po'i ye shes khyad par can rgyud la skyes
NK014(pha)006:3351: rjes su 'jug pa'i phyag rgya nyid //
NK014(pha)006:3352: zil pa'i thig le sngon lam bzhin //
NK014(pha)006:3353: bcu drug phyed phyed thig le gcig /
NK014(pha)006:3354: phan tshun dgod pa'i stabs kyis bstim //
NK014(pha)006:3355: bde ba gnyis pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK014(pha)006:3356: gsum pa'i ye shes dkyil 'khor du //
NK014(pha)006:3357: gsal bar shar bas gyur pa'i sgra //
NK014(pha)006:3359: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK014(pha)006:3361: de ltar bskul tshig gis nyams su myong ba'i don
NK014(pha)006:3362: ngo sprad pas sems nyid don dam 'od gsal du
NK014(pha)006:3363: dwangs pa'i rtags snang lhag pa kun rdzob kyi ye
NK014(pha)006:3364: shes su shar bas lhan skyes bde ba chen po
NK014(pha)006:3365: rgyud la skyes te shes rab ye shes kyi dbang
NK014(pha)006:3369: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK014(pha)006:3370: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi zad
NK014(pha)006:3371: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bden pa chen po'i byin
NK014(pha)006:3372: gyi rlabs kyis / skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa
NK014(pha)006:3373: khyod la ye shes rang gnas kyi dbang bskur bas
NK014(pha)006:3374: shes bya'i dri ma dag nas don dam pa 'gag
NK014(pha)006:3375: med kyi ye shes mngon du rtogs pa'i dbang dam
NK014(pha)006:3377: de nas rdor dril slob bu'i snying gar bzung la //
NK014(pha)006:3378: mi 'gyur ba yi ye shes gnas //
NK014(pha)006:3379: ma btsal phyin pas bde ba'i mchog /
NK014(pha)006:3380: ma bltas gsal ba'i ye shes spyan //
NK014(pha)006:3381: gong na med pas kun gyi rje //
NK014(pha)006:3382: ye shes rang gnas brdal ba la //
NK014(pha)006:3383: mi 'gyur g.yung drung sa thob shog /
NK014(pha)006:3384: ma h+aa gu h+ya b+h+r+aum dz+ny+aa na man+da la dz+ny+aa
NK014(pha)006:3385: na gu h+ya sid+d+hi swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham
NK014(pha)006:3387: de nas dbugs dbyung ba ni /
NK014(pha)006:3388: de ring phan chad bu khyod ni //
NK014(pha)006:3389: rang rig bde la gnas pas na //
NK014(pha)006:3390: rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya ste //
NK014(pha)006:3391: yum dang 'jo ma thams cad la //
NK014(pha)006:3393: rigs su gyur rnams thabs 'di bzung //
NK014(pha)006:3395: dbang phyug rgyal po nyid du nges //
NK014(pha)006:3397: gsum pa dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang ni /
NK014(pha)006:3398: man+dala sngon du 'gro bas bla ma la phyag rgya
NK014(pha)006:3399: mtshan ldan lo bcu gnyis ma rgyud dag par byas
NK014(pha)006:3401: he ru ka dpal khyod la 'dud //
NK014(pha)006:3402: thar lam chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK014(pha)006:3403: de nyid dbang dang dam tshig dang //
NK014(pha)006:3404: mgon po dpa' bor skyabs song ste //
NK014(pha)006:3405: theg chen khang par gzhug pa dang //
NK014(pha)006:3406: mkhyen rab ye shes bdag la stsol //
NK014(pha)006:3408: bu 'dir shog cig ci bde bar //
NK014(pha)006:3409: las spyod rim par 'gro ba dang //
NK014(pha)006:3410: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje bzung //
NK014(pha)006:3411: rdzogs pa'i ye shes bde chen la //
NK014(pha)006:3412: dmigs pa med par gnas phyir du //
NK014(pha)006:3413: ser sna spangs pa'i dang yid kyis //
NK014(pha)006:3414: gtong zhing rang sems brtan por bzung //
NK014(pha)006:3415: ye shes rang gnas rdzogs dbang sbyin //
NK014(pha)006:3417: de nas slob bu'i gung mo g.yas dang phyag rgya'i
NK014(pha)006:3418: gung mo g.yon pa lto sbyar te rat+na'i phreng bas
NK014(pha)006:3419: bcings pa'i rtse nas dbang phyug gi mtheb srin gyis
NK014(pha)006:3420: bzung ste slob ma la gtad par mos la /
NK014(pha)006:3421: bde ba chen po chos kyi sku //
NK014(pha)006:3422: shes rab thabs kyis rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK014(pha)006:3423: 'di dang skye ba thams cad du //
NK014(pha)006:3424: dngos grub bde 'di ma spongs shig /
NK014(pha)006:3425: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK014(pha)006:3426: rdzogs pa'i phyag rgya khyod las byung //
NK014(pha)006:3427: spangs nas rdo rje dbyings phyug rtsa //
NK014(pha)006:3428: dgug dang bsdam pa ma shes na //
NK014(pha)006:3429: rdo rje bskal pa mtha' klas par //
NK014(pha)006:3430: chos sku thob par mi 'gyur ro //
NK014(pha)006:3432: de nas slob ma dang gtad pa'i phyag rgya gnyis
NK014(pha)006:3433: phan tshun 'dod pa'i bstan bcos kyis bde ba rgyas
NK014(pha)006:3434: par byas rjes / slob ma dkyil 'khor gyi gtso
NK014(pha)006:3435: bo bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po badz+ra he
NK014(pha)006:3436: ru kar gsal ba'i gnas lngar khrag 'thung rigs lnga
NK014(pha)006:3437: dang lag pa g.yas g.yon kha dang gsang ba'i phyi
NK014(pha)006:3439: phyag rgya lo bcu gnyis ma yum badz+ra kro d+he
NK014(pha)006:3440: shwa r+ai mar gsal ba'i gnas lngar yum lnga dang
NK014(pha)006:3441: / yan lag bzhi la khro mo bzhi rnams gsal bar gyur /
NK014(pha)006:3449: yab kyi gsang gnas h+aum las ye shes kyi rdo
NK014(pha)006:3450: rje rtse mo lnga pa'i lte bar byang chub kyi
NK014(pha)006:3451: sems dkar por gnas pa'i bu gar phata kyis bkag
NK014(pha)006:3452: cing rwa lnga la nyi ma la gnas pa'i dpa'
NK014(pha)006:3453: bo 'bru lnga / yum gyi mkha' pam las pad+ma
NK014(pha)006:3454: dmar po 'dab ma bzhi pa'i lte bar nyi ma
NK014(pha)006:3455: la rak+ta +aam dmar por gnas pa'i ge sar la
NK014(pha)006:3456: bo 'bru lnga / e / dbus dang 'dab bzhir
NK014(pha)006:3457: zla ba la gnas pa'i dpa' mo 'bru lngas mtshan
NK014(pha)006:3458: bo 'bru lnga / e / par bsam la / sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)006:3459: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa go ham /
NK014(pha)006:3460: a nu r+aa ga ya mye /
NK014(pha)006:3461: zhes sbyor ba'i brdas phan tshun bsnol mar bskul te /
NK014(pha)006:3462: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes phyag rgya bzhis 'khyud sdom sprad nas /
NK014(pha)006:3463: snyoms par zhugs pa'i byang chub kyi sems 'khor lo
NK014(pha)006:3464: bzhir yas babs kyi rim pas dga' ba bcu drug
NK014(pha)006:3465: gi 'gros kyis phyin pa las nyi zla zung 'brel
NK014(pha)006:3467: zla ba'i thig le re re bzhi ye shes lnga'i
NK014(pha)006:3468: nyams dang ldan pas dpe byad brgyad cu rdzogs shing
NK014(pha)006:3469: mngon shes drug kyang shar nas yum gyi rtsa kha
NK014(pha)006:3470: kha mu kha'i rtser nyi zla gnyis 'dres 'khyil ba
NK014(pha)006:3471: de nyid rdo rje nor bur bstim pa h+aum zhes
NK014(pha)006:3472: gyen du ldog pa'i sbyor bas mas brtan gyi dga'
NK014(pha)006:3473: bzhi'i ye shes nyams su myong bar byas pa'i dga'
NK014(pha)006:3474: bzhi'i ye shes re re la yang dga' ba bzhi
NK014(pha)006:3475: bzhi ste bcu drug gi dang po bzhis tshogs lam
NK014(pha)006:3476: dang / de nas re res sbyor mthong /
NK014(pha)006:3477: de nas dgus sgom lam sa dgu rdzogs te /
NK014(pha)006:3478: dga' ba bcu drug gi mtha' ma rang bzhin lhan
NK014(pha)006:3479: cig skyes pa bde ba chen po'i ye shes khyad
NK014(pha)006:3480: par can rgyud la skyes pa de'i tshe na snang
NK014(pha)006:3481: stong gi mthas ma sgribs par gsal bas kun tu
NK014(pha)006:3482: 'od dang / mi shigs pa'i dwangs mas lus thams
NK014(pha)006:3483: cad la khyab cing brtan pas 'khor ba'i skyon gyis
NK014(pha)006:3484: ma gos pas pad+ma can dang /
NK014(pha)006:3485: rtogs tshogs thams cad sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil
NK014(pha)006:3486: 'khor rab 'byams su rang snang bas yi ge 'khor
NK014(pha)006:3488: mdor na thun mong dang khyad par gyi sa lam thams cad rdzogs par byas par mos la /
NK014(pha)006:3490: rdo rje nyi ma thabs kyi rgya /
NK014(pha)006:3491: phung sogs phyag rgya'i tshogs dang ldan //
NK014(pha)006:3492: de zla bsil byed shes rab dngos //
NK014(pha)006:3493: dus gcig ro mnyam thig le che //
NK014(pha)006:3494: sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan rdzogs shing //
NK014(pha)006:3495: zla ba'i ye shes lnga bcu drug /
NK014(pha)006:3496: dpe byad la sogs dpag tu med //
NK014(pha)006:3497: sems shes mngon par shes dang ldan //
NK014(pha)006:3499: gnas nas log pa thim pa'i sgra //
NK014(pha)006:3500: mtha' gnyis ma gos pad+ma can //
NK014(pha)006:3501: sprul pa'i gnas nas bkye ba yis //
NK014(pha)006:3502: bzhi bcu lnga sogs mtha' yas kun //
NK014(pha)006:3503: rang bzhin nyid las rang gsal ba //
NK014(pha)006:3504: bcu gsum yi ge 'khor lo brjod //
NK014(pha)006:3505: d+harma k+aa ya a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK014(pha)006:3506: de ltar bskul tshig gis nyams su myong ba'i don
NK014(pha)006:3507: ngo sprad pas 'khor 'das mnyam nyid bde ba chen
NK014(pha)006:3508: po'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bsgyur te /
NK014(pha)006:3509: mchog tu mi 'gyur ba de kho na nyid kyi don mngon du byas par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)006:3512: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK014(pha)006:3513: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi zad
NK014(pha)006:3514: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bden pa chen po'i byin
NK014(pha)006:3515: gyi rlabs kyis / skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa
NK014(pha)006:3516: khyod la bde ba chen po'i dbang bskur bas sgrib
NK014(pha)006:3517: gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa dag nas skye 'gag
NK014(pha)006:3518: gnyis su med pa zung 'jug don dam pa'i ye
NK014(pha)006:3519: shes mngon du rtogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK014(pha)006:3520: gyi rlabs kyis / gyur cig / de ltar gsang ba b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK014(pha)006:3521: de kho na nyid sems kyi dkyil 'khor du zab
NK014(pha)006:3522: mo'i dbang gsum bskur bas thun mong ma yin pa'i
NK014(pha)006:3523: rdzogs rim rnams nyan sgom nus pa'i skal ba can
NK014(pha)006:3525: de nas dbang ma thob pa dang thob pa'i skyon yon bshad pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:3527: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK014(pha)006:3528: dbang rnams thob par ma byas par //
NK014(pha)006:3529: nyan pa la sogs rtsom pa rnams //
NK014(pha)006:3531: zhes dbang ma thob pa'i skyon dang /
NK014(pha)006:3532: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK014(pha)006:3533: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK014(pha)006:3534: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK014(pha)006:3535: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK014(pha)006:3536: zhes dbang thob pa'i phan yon gsungs te /
NK014(pha)006:3537: de bas na bskyed rdzogs kyi lam zab mo nyams su len pa la /
NK014(pha)006:3538: dang por dbang nod pa shin tu nas gces pa yin no //
NK014(pha)006:3539: des dbang bskur ba'i rim pa dngos song nas rjes
NK014(pha)006:3540: kyi rim pa la bzhi yod pa'i dang po dbang
NK014(pha)006:3541: rtags sbyin zhing bka' bsgo ba ni /
NK014(pha)006:3542: slob ma'i lag tu rdo rje gtad de gsor du bcug la /
NK014(pha)006:3543: sangs rgyas kun gyi rdo rje'i dbang //
NK014(pha)006:3544: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK014(pha)006:3545: sangs rgyas kun tu rab bsgrub phyir //
NK014(pha)006:3546: rdo rje 'di ni khyod kyis longs //
NK014(pha)006:3547: dril bu gtad de dkrol du bcug la /
NK014(pha)006:3548: rdo rje dril bu rig pa 'dzin //
NK014(pha)006:3549: thabs dang shes rab dbang chen te //
NK014(pha)006:3551: chos la 'dod bzhin dbang bskur ro //
NK014(pha)006:3552: de nas slar yang rdor dril bsnol nas slob bu'i lag pa g.yas g.yon du gtad de /
NK014(pha)006:3553: rdo rje gsor zhing dril bu dkrol du bcug la /
NK014(pha)006:3554: badz+ra g+han+de a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK014(pha)006:3558: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK014(pha)006:3559: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi zad
NK014(pha)006:3560: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bden pa chen po'i byin
NK014(pha)006:3561: gyi rlabs kyis / skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa
NK014(pha)006:3562: khyod la dbang rtags rdo rje dang dril bu gtad
NK014(pha)006:3563: de dbang bskur bas thabs dang shes rab gnyis su
NK014(pha)006:3564: med pas 'gro ba sems can gyi don rgyun mi
NK014(pha)006:3565: chad par byed pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK014(pha)006:3566: gyi rlabs kyis / cig / de nas dbang phyug
NK014(pha)006:3567: dbang khri la 'dug pa'i zhabs g.yas pa la mgo
NK014(pha)006:3569: de ring phan chad bu khyod kyi //
NK014(pha)006:3570: he ru ka dpal nga yin pas //
NK014(pha)006:3571: nga yis ji skad bsgo ba bzhin //
NK014(pha)006:3572: bu khyod kyis ni bya dgos so //
NK014(pha)006:3574: gnyis pa bum chu blud cing smon lam gdab pa ni /
NK014(pha)006:3575: dbang phyug bzhengs te dbus kyi bum pa btegs la /
NK014(pha)006:3576: dbu rgyan cod pan phreng ba dang //
NK014(pha)006:3577: go cha rgyal mtshan phyag rgya dang //
NK014(pha)006:3578: gdugs dang bum pa bza' btung dang //
NK014(pha)006:3579: snying po lnga yi dbang bskur na //
NK014(pha)006:3580: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK014(pha)006:3581: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK014(pha)006:3582: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK014(pha)006:3583: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK014(pha)006:3585: tish+tha badz+ra zhes dbang rnams brtan par bya /
NK014(pha)006:3587: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK014(pha)006:3588: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi zad
NK014(pha)006:3589: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bden pa chen po'i byin
NK014(pha)006:3590: gyi rlabs kyis / zhes bden stobs brjod pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK014(pha)006:3591: bdag rdo rje slob dpon che ge mos che ge
NK014(pha)006:3592: mo la sogs pa'i slob bu rnams la sgyu 'phrul
NK014(pha)006:3594: dus 'di phyin chad ngan song gsum la sogs pa'i
NK014(pha)006:3595: sdug bsngal thams cad dang bral nas mtho ris kyi
NK014(pha)006:3596: bde ba phan sum tshogs pa dang ldan te /
NK014(pha)006:3597: de las kyang rgyal ba'i sras rigs phun sum tshogs
NK014(pha)006:3598: pa'i sras su nges par dbang gi 'bras bu ma
NK014(pha)006:3599: lus pa la dbang thob nas /
NK014(pha)006:3600: srid pa'i sems can mtha' dag gi don yongs su rdzogs par byed par gyur cig /
NK014(pha)006:3601: yul phyogs 'di la sogs te rgyal khams thams cad du dus kyi 'khrug pa zhi bar gyur cig /
NK014(pha)006:3602: mtshon gyi bskal pa nyams par gyur cig /
NK014(pha)006:3603: mi nad dang phyugs nad thams cad rgyun chad par gyur cig /
NK014(pha)006:3605: lo phyugs rtag tu legs te sems can thams cad
NK014(pha)006:3606: bde skyid phun sum tshogs pa'i skal ba dang ldan
NK014(pha)006:3607: par gyur cig / gsum pa dbang phyug gi dbang bsab cing slob bu'i lus bslu ba ni /
NK014(pha)006:3608: dbang phyug bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po dpal
NK014(pha)006:3609: he ru kar gsal ba'i thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od
NK014(pha)006:3610: zer 'phros pas dbang rdzas kyi rab gnas kyi lha
NK014(pha)006:3612: slar yang h+aum zhes brjod cing bskur gnas rnams su dbang rdzas rnams gtugs pas /
NK014(pha)006:3613: lha rnams 'od du zhu ba so so'i mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu la thim /
NK014(pha)006:3614: slar yang thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od zer 'phros pas
NK014(pha)006:3615: mdun gyi nam mkhar dpang po'i tshul du bzhugs pa'i
NK014(pha)006:3616: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa thams cad
NK014(pha)006:3617: 'od du zhu nas dbang phyug la thim pas sngar
NK014(pha)006:3618: bas kyang nus pa cher skyes shing gzi 'od 'bar
NK014(pha)006:3619: bar bsam mo // de nas slob bu rnams kyis
NK014(pha)006:3620: phyag sngon du 'gro bas ci 'byor ba'i dngos pos
NK014(pha)006:3623: gnyis med rgyal ba'i mchog la rab gnas shing //
NK014(pha)006:3624: sku gsung thugs kyi rol ba cir ston pa'i //
NK014(pha)006:3625: bla med sman pa'i rgyal po dgongs su gsol //
NK014(pha)006:3626: zang zing rdzas kyi dgos pas ma brel kyang //
NK014(pha)006:3627: bdag 'dzin sdug bsngal rtog pas bcings pa yi //
NK014(pha)006:3628: 'khor ba'i 'dam rdzab klong nas drang ba'i phyir //
NK014(pha)006:3629: 'byor pas dmigs pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK014(pha)006:3631: bzhi pa gtang rag gis mchod cing yon dbul ba ni /
NK014(pha)006:3632: slob bu'i gtso bos ka p+aa la mtshan ldan bdud
NK014(pha)006:3633: rtsis bkang ba mar chol dang bcas pa btegs la
NK014(pha)006:3634: / khyod ni ye nas sku gsung thugs kyi dpal //
NK014(pha)006:3635: dpal gyi phyag rgya mang po thob pa'i phyir //
NK014(pha)006:3636: dus gsum kun tu sangs rgyas yin pa'i rtags //
NK014(pha)006:3637: rdo rje che mchog khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)006:3638: ces dbang phyug gi zhal du drang zhing ci 'byor ba'i yon dbul /
NK014(pha)006:3639: rjes dam tshig khas blang ba /
NK014(pha)006:3641: dge ba bsngo zhing shis pa brjod pas kyang mtha' brgyan par bya'o //
NK014(pha)006:3642: rjes kyi cho ga rnams kyang sgrub dkyil bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK014(pha)006:3643: shin tu gsang ba lhan skyes bde ba'i dngos //
NK014(pha)006:3644: rnam pa kun ldan chos kun snying po'i bcud //
NK014(pha)006:3645: dus gsum rgyal ba'i dgongs don de kho na //
NK014(pha)006:3646: 'khrul med ji bzhin nyid ston nges pa'i lam //
NK014(pha)006:3647: rang snang khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad lha'i //
NK014(pha)006:3648: ye shes rdo rje'i rol mor longs spyod phyir //
NK014(pha)006:3649: rim gnyis rin chen khang par 'jug pa'i sgo //
NK014(pha)006:3650: ston byed tshangs pa'i gad rgyangs dbyangs su blangs //
NK014(pha)006:3651: gting dpag dka' ba rgyud don rgya mtsho'i mtha' //
NK014(pha)006:3652: byis pa'ii ngang tshul bdag ltas ci ste mtshon //
NK014(pha)006:3653: 'on kyang sngon byon mkhas pa'i bstan bcos dang //
NK014(pha)006:3654: dam pa'i gsung rgyun ji bzhin yi ger spel //
NK014(pha)006:3655: 'dir 'bad dge ba nyin mor byed pa'i gzis //
NK014(pha)006:3656: blo gsal snying gi pad+mo cher bzhad pas //
NK014(pha)006:3657: skal ldan rkang drug tshogs rnams yid 'phrog ste //
NK014(pha)006:3658: legs byas sbrang rtsi'i dpal la spyod gyur cig /
NK014(pha)006:3659: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba khro bo bsdus pa'i dbang gi
NK014(pha)006:3660: cho ga khrag 'thung rdo rje'i gad rgyangs zhes bya
NK014(pha)006:3661: ba 'di yang rang gzhan mang por phan 'dod dang
NK014(pha)006:3662: / nye char rigs kyi gcung 'gyur med yid bzhin
NK014(pha)006:3663: legs par grub pa'i gsung gis kyang bskul ma btab
NK014(pha)006:3664: par brten drin can bla ma gter bdag gling pa
NK014(pha)006:3665: mched kyi zhabs rdul spyi bos len pa smyos ban
NK014(pha)006:3666: pad+ma 'gyur med rgya mtsho mi pham rnam rgyal rdo
NK014(pha)006:3667: rjes rang lo nyer gcig pa mi zad pa'i lo
NK014(pha)006:3668: smin drug zla ba'i dkar phyogs kyi gral tshes dge
NK014(pha)006:3669: bar zhi khro'i cho ga thun mong ba rnams 'jug
NK014(pha)006:3670: pa bde ba'i phyir zhi ba'i dbang chog nyid gzhir
NK014(pha)006:3671: byas te 'og min o rgyan smin grol gling gi
NK014(pha)006:3672: bla brang chos 'khor lhun por sug bris su sbyar
